ous%20quarter%2C%20its%20earnings%20report%20on%20January%2031%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENYCB%20also%20set%20aside%20%24552%20million%20to%20cover%20loan%20losses%20%E2%80%94%20a%20huge%20jump%20from%20%2462%20million%20in%20the%20third%20quarter.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20slashed%20its%20dividend%20from%2017%20cents%20to%205%20cents%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20build%20up%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20efforts%20to%20clean%20up%20its%20finances%20stemmed%20in%20part%20from%20it%20crossing%20%24100%20billion%20in%20assets%20following%20two%20acquisitions%20in%20the%20past%2018%20months.%20It%20bought%20deposits%20and%20some%20loans%20from%20Signature%20Bank%2C%20which%20collapsed%20last%20spring%20along%20with%20Silicon%20Valley%20Bank%20and%20Silvergate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBanks%20of%20that%20size%20are%20subject%20to%20greater%20regulatory%20insight.%20Indeed%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-05%2Fnycb-s-tense-talks-with-watchdog-led-to-moves-that-rocked-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBloomberg%20reported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20regulators%20have%20been%20pushing%20the%20lender%20to%20improve%20its%20capital%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoody's%20slashed%20NYCB's%20credit%20rating%20to%20junk%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-07%2Fnew-york-community-bancorp-s-credit-grade-cut-to-junk-by-moody-s%3Fsrnd%3Dpremium%26embedded-checkout%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20credit-ratings%20agency%20cited%20myriad%20financial%20risks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20governance%20issues%20after%20the%20departure%20of%20audit%20and%20risk%20executives%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENYCB's%20deteriorating%20financials%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20Moody's%20cut%2C%20spurred%20investors%20to%20slash%20its%20stock%20price%20by%2060%25%20in%20five%20days%20to%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%201997%2C%20reducing%20its%20market%20capitalization%20by%20%244.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENYCB%20sought%20to%20reassure%20Wall%20Street%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnew-york-community-bancorp-inc-issues-current-liquidity-and-deposit-information-302055530.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereleasing%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20unaudited%20financial%20information%20as%20of%20February%205.%20The%20bank's%20deposits%20have%20grown%20this%20year%20to%20about%20%2483%20billion%2C%20with%20insured%20and%20collateralized%20deposits%20making%20up%2072%25%20of%20the%20total.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20reported%20%2437.3%20billion%20in%20total%20liquidity%2C%20exceeding%20its%20uninsured%20deposits%2C%20and%20had%20about%20%2417%20billion%20in%20cash.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20decisive%20actions%20to%20fortify%20our%20balance%20sheet%20and%20strengthen%20our%20risk%20management%20processes%20during%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Thomas%20Cangemi%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20its%20goal%20was%20to%20enhance%20its%20risk%20management%20to%20match%20its%20increased%20size%20and%20complexity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20noted%20that%20NYCB%20is%20working%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20new%20chief%20risk%20officer%20and%20chief%20audit%20executive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20are%20investors%20worried%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENYCB's%20unexpected%20loss%2C%20combined%20with%20its%20decision%20to%20pare%20shareholder%20payouts%20and%20make%20a%20large%20provision%20for%20bad%20loans%2C%20has%20fanned%20fears%20that%20its%20loans%20and%20assets%20in%20the%20commercial%20and%20multi-family%20real%20estate%20sectors%20are%20in%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20undoubtedly%20wary%20of%20that%2