0many%20ways%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F611335%2Fmg-launches-mg4-electric-europe-with-28420-euro-base-price%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMG%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20new%20Mini.%20Its%20products%20are%20new%2C%20shiny%20and%20come%20with%20tech%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20early%20cars%20could%20never%20dream%20of.%20And%20yet%2C%20there's%20a%20large%20group%20of%20people%20who%20don't%20think%20nu-MG%20is%20%26quot%3Bproper.%26quot%3B%20Those%20people%20need%20to%20drive%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F675246%2F2023-mg4-ev-xpower-previewed-429-hp-awd-electric-hot-hatch%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMG4%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20first%2C%20some%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20MG%20changed%20hands%20to%20China's%20SAIC%20back%20in%20the%20Aughts%2C%20eyebrows%20raised%20for%20sure.%20Back%20then%2C%20tiny%20hatches%20that%20fell%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Baggressively%20OK%26quot%3B%20category%20were%20the%20order%20of%20the%20day%2C%20as%20was%20the%20old%20MG%20TF%20sports%20car%2C%20of%20course.%20But%20nothing%20the%20company%20produced%20seemed%20to%20justify%20the%20endless%20MG%20branded%20swag%20you%20could%20buy%20on%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20soldiered%20on%20with%20cars%20that%20were%20just%20fine%20enough.%20Keenly%20priced%2C%20not%20terrible%20to%20drive%2C%20not%20terrible%20to%20look%20at%2C%20but%20nothing%20you'd%20sit%20awake%20thinking%20about%20for%20years%20to%20come.%20(And%20in%20other%20places%2C%20like%20North%20America%2C%20the%20MG%20brand%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgrassrootsmotorsports.com%2Farticles%2Fmgb-vintage-views%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eknown%20for%20tiny%20vintage%20sports%20cars%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20little%20else.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%202022%2C%20the%20MG4%20arrived.%20It%20was%20based%20on%20a%20new%20purpose-built%20EV%20platform%20with%20a%20look%20that%20meant%20it%20wouldn't%20blend%20in%2C%20respectable%20ranges%20from%20sensibly%20sized%20batteries%2C%20acceptable%20performance%20and%2C%20perhaps%20most%20importantly%2C%20a%20keen%20price%20point.%20It%20was%20something%20of%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air.%20Its%20rivals%20were%20all%20more%20expensive%2C%20though%20more%20familiar.%20That%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20protect%20their%20market%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIf%20you%20head%20to%20certain%20bits%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20the%20MG4%20is%20absolutely%20everywhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStand%20on%20a%20street%20corner%20and%20you'll%20likely%20see%20at%20least%20a%20handful%20in%20no%20time%20at%20all%E2%80%94private%20cars%2C%20fleet%20drivers%2C%20and%20Ubers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20do%20normal%20people%20like%20it%2C%20scruffy%20journalists%20like%20it%2C%20too.%20It's%20won%20a%20raft%20of%20gongs%20for%20being%2C%20as%20the%20clich%C3%A9%20goes%2C%20a%20'lil%20bit%20Goldilocks.%20After%20so%20much%20love%20has%20been%20heaped%20on%20it%20by%20various%20colleagues%2C%20I%20figured%20it%20was%20time%20to%20give%20it%20a%20go.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20MG%20MG4%20Xpower%20on%20the%20road.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c2856943bb77284ba4264b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202024%20MG%20MG4%20XPower.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Goy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMG%20decided%20to%20send%20me%20the%20MG4%20XPower%2C%20the%20fastest%20one%20you%20can%20get%2C%20as%20I%20am%20a%20hooligan.%20With%20a%20motor%20on%20each%20axle%2C%20it%20kicks%20out%20429%20hp%20and%20443%20lb-ft%20in%20total.%20That's%20enough%20to%20get%20the%203968-lb%20car%20to%2062%20in%203.8%20seconds%2C%20roughly%20as%20quick%20as%20an%20Audi%20RS%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%2061.6-kWh%20(usable)%20battery%20will%20get%20you%20just%20shy%20of%20240%20miles%20on%20a%20charge%20on%20the%20more%20generous%20European%20WLTP%20cycle%2C%20which%20is%20plenty%20for%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMG%20isn't%20asking%20silly%20money%20for%20it%2C%20about%20%C2%A336%2C500%2C%20or%20%2446%2C500%20at%20today's%20exchange%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEuro%20EV%20manufacturers%20have%20been%20looking%20for%20an%20electric%20take%20on%20the%20hot%20hatch%20for%20years%2C%20and%20you'd%20be%20forgiven%20for%20thinking%20the%20MG4%20XPower%20is%20exactly%20that.%20It's%20got%20the%20grunt%20(though%20a%20124mph%20top%20speed)%2C%20and%20it%20comes%20with%2018-inch%20wheels%2C%20bright%20brake%20calipers%20wrapped%20around%20big%20brakes%2C%20stiff%20suspension%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20trickery%20to%20make%20sure%20power%20goes%20where%20it%20needs%20to%20go.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20outside%2C%20it's%20a%20looker.%20Not%20so%20out%20there%20to%20alienate%20more%20traditional%20buyers%2C%20but%20not%20as%20forgettable%20as%20the%20old%20MGs.%20Inside%20it's%E2%80%A6%20pretty%20sparse%2C%20actually.%20There's%20a%20modest%20screen%20for%20infotainment%20duties%2C%20a%20small%20one%20above%20the%20steering%20wheel%20for%20speedo%20work%20and%20a%20small%20center%20console%20housing%20a%20gear%20selector%20and%20a%20wireless%20phone%20charging%20tray.%20Cubbyholes%20and%20the%20odd%20USB%20slot%20aside%2C%20there's%20not%20much%20else%20to%20shout%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20the%20MG%20MG4%20XPower.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c286ab43bb77284ba426db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20the%20MG%20MG4%20XPower.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Goy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20with%20Apple%20CarPlay%2C%20though%20the%20cabled%20connection%20was%20a%20little%20temperamental.%20MG's%20own%20UI%20is%20pleasant%20enough%20to%20use%2C%20but%2C%20again%2C%20it's%20a%20budget%20car%2C%20don't%20expect%20the%20world.%20Its%20touchscreen%20isn't%20the%20quickest%20to%20respond%20to%20prods%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20agree%20with%20being%20angry-prodded%20until%20it%20does%20what%20you%20want%20it%20to%20either.%20If%20you%20decide%20to%20wirelessly%20charge%20your%20phone%2C%20good%20for%20you!%20It's%20a%20bit%20slow%2C%20and%20can%20be%20a%20touch%20hit%20and%20miss.%20MG's%20interior%20designers%20must%20not%20have%20known%20about%20the%200-60%20time.%20Give%20it%20the%20beans%20from%20the%20lights%20and%20your%20phone%20flies%20around%20the%20car.%20It's%20not%20ideal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOn%20a%20cruise%20around%20town%20it's%20quiet%2C%20calm%2C%20serene%2C%20and%20quick%20if%20you%20want%20it%20to%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20400%20hp%20in%20a%20Golf-sized%20car%20is%20more%20than%20adequate%2C%20frankly.%20Its%20steering%20isn't%20all%20that%20sharp%2C%20which%20is%20something%20of%20a%20left%20down%2C%20and%20its%20suspension%20isn't%20too%20hateful%20over%20London's%20potholed%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20handy%20is%20its%20one-pedal%20drive%20mode%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20exactly%20what%20you'd%20expect%2C%20sure%2C%20but%20it%20works%20well%20enough%20that%20only%20an%20errant%20Uber%20Eats%20moped%20rider%20with%20a%20death%20wish%20will%20cause%20you%20to%20lurch%20for%20the%20brake.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20MG%20MG4%20XPower%20on%20the%20road.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c28d6243bb77284ba42b5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDriving%20the%20MG%20MG4%20XPower%20on%20the%20road.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Goy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20it%20on%20the%20highway%20is%20much%20the%20same%E2%80%A6%20it's%20a%20decent%20way%20to%20get%20around.%20You're%20neatly%20insulated%20from%20the%20world%2C%20and%20should%20you%20need%20to%20make%20progress%20you%20can%2C%20but%20that%20comes%20at%20a%20cost%3A%20range.%20Yeah%2C%20it's%20much%20the%20same%20as%20a%20gas%20car%3A%20Hoof%20it%20and%20you%20use%20more%20juice%2C%20but%20combine%20that%20with%20a%20cooler%20British%20winter%20and%20a%20near-240-mile%20range%20vanishes%20rather%20quickly.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20time%20I%20had%20in%20it%20the%20little%20MG%20barely%20breached%203.0m%2FkWh%2C%20which%20was%20a%20cause%20for%20concern%20when%20it%20came%20time%20to%20find%20a%20charger%20on%20the%20UK's%20notoriously%20woeful%20network%20of%20public%20chargers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhere%20MG%20wants%20it%20to%20work%20is%20twisty%20roads%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEurope%20is%20the%20home%20of%20the%20hot%20hatch%2C%20and%20to%20get%20it%20right%20at%20this%20price%20point%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20boon.%20MG's%20had%20a%20good%20'ol%20crack%20of%20the%20whip%2C%20arguably%20a%20better%20go%20than%20Euro%20hot%20hatches%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F577491%2Fcupra-born-eboost%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECupra%20Born%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20falls%20a%20bit%20flat.%20You%20can%20hustle%20it%20for%20sure%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20really%20suited%20for%20silliness.%20All%20the%20ingredients%20are%20allegedly%20there%20but%20they%20don't%20quite%20combine%20to%20make%20a%20greater%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20MG%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20make%20a%20hot%20hatch%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20it%20made%20a%20brisk%20EV%2C%20and%20the%20MG4%20is%20rather%20decent%20at%20being%20one%20of%20those.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EShould%20America%20be%20jealous%20of%20the%20MG4%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20outside%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20EV%20with%20a%20battery%20packing%20fewer%20than%20100kWh%2C%20and%20a%20footprint%20smaller%20than%20a%20house%20would%20seem%20alien%2C%20but%20in%20reality%E2%80%A6%20it%20would%20probably%20go%20down%20well%20in%20the%20sunnier%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20looker%2C%20quick%2C%20and%20gets%20you%20to%20work%20and%20back%20on%20a%20charge%20with%20ease.%20If%20MG%20could%20get%20it%20to%20America%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%2C%20it'd%20be%20a%20decent%20option%E2%80%94though%20US%20tariffs%20on%20China's%20cars%20probably%20keep%20that%20off%20the%20table%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPity%2C%20that.%20More%C2%A0cheap%20EVs%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20in%20the%20meantime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlex%20Goy%20is%20a%20longtime%20motoring%20journalist%20and%20host%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Ffeatures%2Fcategory%2Fpodcast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EInsideEVs%20Podcast%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20He%20is%20based%20in%20London.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmg-mg4-xpower-ev-car-review-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707301082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c2852d43bb77284ba42631%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmg-mg4-xpower-ev-car-review-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20MG%20could%20get%20their%20MG4%20to%20America%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%2C%20it'd%20be%20a%20decent%20option.%20It's%20a%20looker%2C%20quick%2C%20and%20gets%20drivers%20where%20they%20need%20to%20go.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alex%20Goy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmg-mg4-xpower-ev-car-review-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Now%2C%20govt%20to%20lease%20strategic%20oil%20reserve%20space%20to%20pvt%20cos%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707301003000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107489061%2Cimgsize-14380.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fnow-