0%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-vault-track-ranking-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1989%20(Taylor's%20Version)%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20was%20released%20in%20October%202023%2C%20iHeart%20played%20original%20versions%20of%20Swift's%20songs%20an%20average%20of%20three%20times%20a%20day%20on%20the%20six%20stations%20BI%20looked%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FKH0uK%2F6%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22iHeart%20original%20version%20plays%20post-Taylor's%20version%20releases%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20stations%20BI%20examined%20are%20part%20of%20the%20largest%20markets%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20they're%20merely%20a%20fraction%20of%20iHeart's%20empire.%20iHeart%20has%20more%20than%20100%20Top%2040%20and%20pop%20stations%20in%20its%20portfolio.%20It%20also%20owns%20stations%20in%20other%20genres%2C%20like%20adult%20contemporary%2C%20that%20often%20play%20Swift%20songs.%20This%20means%20the%20true%20number%20of%20non-Taylor's%20Version%20of%20songs%20played%20by%20iHeart%20stations%20is%20likely%20much%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20BI%20described%20its%20findings%2C%20iHeartMedia%20said%20it%20would%20take%20steps%20across%20its%20entire%20network%20to%20make%20sure%20erroneous%20plays%20didn't%20happen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20played%20Taylor's%20Version%20songs%20millions%20of%20times%20across%20our%20broadcast%20radio%20stations%20and%20they're%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20that%20Taylor's%20Version%20songs%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20we%20play%2C%20so%20they%20are%20scrubbing%20through%20our%20system%20and%20doing%20another%20thorough%20sweep%20to%20remove%20any%20incorrect%20versions%2C%26quot%3B%20Wendy%20Goldberg%2C%20iHeart's%20chief%20communications%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Swift%20didn't%20respond%20to%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EiHeartMedia's%20radio%20empire%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20radio%20industry%2C%20iHeartMedia%20is%20an%20800-pound%20gorilla.%20With%20stations%20broadcasting%20nearly%20every%20genre%20of%20music%20in%20every%20major%20US%20city%2C%20the%20company%20says%20that%2090%25%20of%20Americans%20hear%20its%20programming%20each%20month.%20It%20also%20hosts%20and%20airs%20live%20entertainment%2C%20like%20the%20hourlong%20release%20party%20for%20Swift's%20album%20%26quot%3BReputation%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20aired%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iheartmedia.com%2Fpress%2Fiheartmedia-presents-iheartradio-reputation-album-release-party-taylor-swift-presented-att%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E126%20stations%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202017%20and%20the%20iHeartRadio%20Music%20Awards%20(where%20Swift%20reigns%20as%20the%20most-awarded%20artist).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-solo-written-songs-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESwift%20writes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20of%20her%20own%20songs%2C%20so%20she%20gets%20paid%20no%20matter%20which%20version%20is%20played%20on%20the%20radio.%20But%20by%20buying%20(and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscooter-braun-sells-taylor-swift-masters-300-million-big-machine-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling)%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20master%20recordings%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20her%20will%2C%20others%20still%20stand%20to%20profit%20from%20record%20sales%20and%20downloads%20of%20the%20originals%2C%20something%20Swift%20was%20determined%20to%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECasey%20Rae%2C%20a%20music-business%20professor%20and%20former%20programming%20executive%20for%20SiriusXM%2C%20said%20it's%20unusual%20for%20radio%20stations%20to%20make%20a%20public%20promise%20like%20iHeart%20did%2C%20but%20it%20was%20likely%20done%20with%20Swift's%20vast%20fan%20base%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20they're%20just%20happy%20to%20live%20in%20a%20world%20with%20more%20Taylor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20political%20component%20to%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20check%20iHeart's%20compliance%20with%20its%20commitment%2C%20Business%20Insider%20contacted%20several%20media-monitoring%20services%20that%20said%20they%20could%20monitor%20radio%20plays.%20Songwriters%20and%20others%20in%20the%20music%20industry%20use%20these%20services%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20aren't%20being%20stiffed%20on%20royalties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20list%20of%2072%20tracks%20that%20Swift%20has%20rereleased%20as%20Taylor's%20Versions%2C%20BI%20worked%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facrcloud.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EACRcloud%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20uses%20acoustic%20fingerprinting%20similar%20to%20what%20the%20so%20powers%20Shazam%20to%20analyze%20Swift's%20airplay%20going%20back%20to%20March%202021%2C%20shortly%20before%20Swift%20released%20her%20first%20rerecorded%20album%2C%20%26quot%3BFearless%20(Taylor's%20Version).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20stations%20that%20played%20the%20most%20Swift%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ACRcloud%20data%20analyzed%20by%20BI%2C%20are%20iHeart-owned%3A%20KBIG-FM%2C%20KIIS-FM%2C%20and%20KOST-FM%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20WKSC-FM%20and%20WLIT-FM%20in%20Chicago%2C%20and%20WLTW-FM%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iHeart%20stations%20in%20BI's%20sample%20played%20just%20over%2054%2C000%20Taylor%20Swift%20songs%20from%20March%202021%20through%20December%202023.%20The%20data%20shows%20626%20of%20those%20plays%20%E2%80%94%20about%201.2%25%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20were%20of%20the%20non-Taylor's%20Version%20of%20a%20song%20for%20which%20a%20Taylor's%20Version%20had%20been%20released%20at%20least%20a%20day%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EiHeart%20stations%20most%20often%20played%20the%20original%20version%20of%20the%20songs%20%26quot%3BI%20Knew%20You%20Were%20Trouble%2C%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20album%20%26quot%3BRed%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BLove%20Story%2C%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20album%20%26quot%3BFearless%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20a%20Taylor's%20Version%20was%20available.%20These%20two%20songs%20accounted%20for%20about%20half%20of%20the%20626%20non-Taylor's%20Version%20spins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20version%20of%20%26quot%3BShake%20It%20Off%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Swift's%20latest%20rerecorded%20album%2C%20%26quot%3B1989%20(Taylor's%20Version)%2C%26quot%3B%20released%20in%20October%202023%20%E2%80%94%20was%20spun%2036%20times%20on%20iHeart%20stations%20in%20the%20roughly%20two%20months%20after%20the%20Taylor's%20Version%20of%20the%20song%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOther%20radio%20stations%20were%20less%20likely%20to%20play%20Taylor's%20Versions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20couldn't%20find%20any%20other%20radio-station%20operators%20that%20promised%20to%20play%20only%20Taylor's%20Versions.%20But%20iHeart%20played%20original%20versions%20at%20a%20lower%20rate%20than%20its%20competitors%3B%20about%202%25%20of%20the%2031%2C690%20spins%20on%20Audacy%20stations%20in%20BI's%20sample%20were%20of%20original%20versions%20of%20songs%20for%20which%20a%20Taylor's%20Version%20existed.%20On%20SiriusXM%2C%20the%20rate%20was%20nearly%204.9%25.%20On%20all%20other%20stations%2C%20amounting%20to%20over%2020%2C000%20plays%2C%20the%20rate%20was%207%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20terms%20of%20sheer%20numbers%2C%20the%20erroneous%20plays%20by%20iHeart%20are%20almost%20certainly%20higher%20than%20the%20few%20hundred%20BI%20found.%20Its%20website%20lists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iheartmedia.com%2Fstations%3Fgenre%3DTop%2B40%2B%2526%2BPop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E108%20radio%20stations%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BTop%2040%20%26amp%3B%20Pop%26quot%3B%20category.%20If%20these%20stations%20played%20Swift's%20original%20recordings%20instead%20of%20her%20rerecordings%20at%20a%20rate%20similar%20to%20the%20six%20iHeart%20stations%20BI%20analyzed%2C%20the%20company%20would%20have%20violated%20its%20promise%20over%2011%2C000%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20iHeart%20made%20the%20promise%20to%20Swift%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20promised%20BI%20it%20would%20scrub%20the%20non-Taylor's%20Versions%20it%20was%20still%20playing%20%E2%80%94%20shows%20the%20cultural%20weight%20Swift%20carries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20social%20phenomenon%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%26quot%3B%20Rae%2C%20the%20former%20satellite-radio%20executive%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BHer%20cultural%20stature%20is%20such%20that%20she%20can%20bend%20things%20to%20different%20outcomes%20than%20mere%20mortals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiheartradio-taylor-swift-taylors-version-promise-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707300421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c24f9a6fcb546d2d4c893f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiheartradio-taylor-swift-taylors-version-promise-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22iHeartMedia%2C%20America's%20biggest%20radio%20network%2C%20promised%20Taylor%20Swift%20it%20would%20stick%20to%20%26quot%3BTaylor's%20Version%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20songs.%20Data%20analysis%20shows%20it%20didn't.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jack%20Newsham%2CLily%20Oberstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiheartradio-taylor-swift-taylors-version-promise-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HDFC%20Bank%20raises%20loan%20interest%20rates%3B%20All%20details