ars%20later%2C%20I%20approached%20my%20aunt%2C%20who%20owned%20the%20land%20by%20default%2C%20and%20asked%20her%20if%20she'd%20let%20me%20buy%20it%20from%20her.%20She%20wasn't%20going%20to%20do%20anything%20with%20the%20land%2C%20so%20she%20said%20I%20could%20have%20it.%20I%20bought%20it%20for%20a%20handshake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20acquired%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fcamping-essentials-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecamping%20gear%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20started%20going%20once%20a%20month.%20There%20was%20nothing%20on%20the%20land%20but%20an%20old%20trailer%20filled%20with%20junk.%20I%20would%20sit%20on%20the%20deck%20my%20grandfather%20had%20built%20around%20the%20trailer%20and%20stare%20at%20the%20mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20gutted%20the%20trailer%20and%20put%20some%20flooring%20down%20over%20the%20asbestos%20to%20make%20it%20livable%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20the%20structure%20wouldn't%20last%20many%20more%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20loved%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20yurt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20yurt%20at%20night%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c114156fcb546d2d4c22f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20yurt%20at%20night.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cami%20Ostman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyurts-the-stylish-house-design-that-youve-probably-never-heard-of-2012-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eyurt%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20circular%20tentlike%20dome%20dwelling%20made%20of%20felt%20or%20skins%20stretched%20over%20a%C2%A0collapsible%C2%A0framework%2C%20traditionally%20used%20by%C2%A0nomadic%20people%20in%20Mongolia%2C%20Siberia%2C%20and%20Turkey.%20I%20liked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouples-lives-modern-yurt-avoid-rent-portland-oregon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20idea%20of%20a%20yurt%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20could%20go%20up%20fast%20and%20was%20somewhat%20insulated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20and%20found%20a%20company%20called%20Pacific%20Yurts%20to%20buy%20the%20materials%20from%20for%20just%20under%20%2419%2C000%2C%20which%20I%20paid%20off%20in%20installments.%20I%20talked%20my%20brothers%20and%20dad%20into%20helping%20me%20build%20it.%20We%20all%20read%20the%20detailed%20instructions%20thoroughly%20and%20watched%20numerous%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20built%20a%20plywood%20platform%20cut%20into%20a%2024-foot-diameter%20circle.%20We%20then%20installed%20a%20drip%20edge%20%E2%80%94%20a%20board%20that%20stands%20up%20an%20inch%20and%20a%20half%20around%20the%20platform%20that%20holds%20in%20the%20main%20structure%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lattice%20wall%20made%20of%20wood%C2%A0%E2%80%94%C2%A0around%20the%20perimeter.%20We%20covered%20ours%20with%20wool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20took%20a%20whole%20weekend%20to%20build%2C%20and%20then%20the%20yurt%20took%20another%20weekend.%20When%20it%20was%20completely%20built%2C%20we%20were%20exhausted%2C%20and%20I%20wept%20with%20joy%20to%20see%20my%20dream%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20yurt%20became%20my%202nd%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20living%20room%20in%20a%20yurt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c1144f43bb77284ba39116%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20the%20yurt.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cami%20Ostman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stay%20two%20to%20five%20nights%20at%20a%20time%20and%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20week%20at%20my%20condo%20in%20Shoreline%2C%20a%20northern%20suburb%20of%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20for%20%26quot%3Bhippy%20chic%26quot%3B%20decor.%20I%20found%20sofas%20and