ing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Buolamwini%20said.%20%26quot%3BProtecting%20our%20essence%3B%20protecting%20what's%20human%20is%20protecting%20our%20essence.%20Let's%20be%20still%20and%20recognize%20what%20makes%20us%20human.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funmasking-ai-review-joy-buolamwini-big-tech-ai-bias-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707300001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c26bb443bb77284ba41448%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funmasking-ai-review-joy-buolamwini-big-tech-ai-bias-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Unmasking%20AI'%20by%20Joy%20Buolamwini%20gives%20a%20human%20perspective%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20shares%20the%20author's%20story%20of%20taking%20Big%20Tech%20to%20task%20on%20AI%20bias.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmelton%40insider.com%20(Monica%20Melton)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funmasking-ai-review-joy-buolamwini-big-tech-ai-bias-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Box%20Office%20Preview%3A%20Can%208%20Films%20Deliver%20a%20%241%20Billion%20Lunar%20New%20Year%20Sequel%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707300000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FMixCollage-06-Feb-2024-06-53-PM-2873-cr-res.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235899229%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eight%20Chinese-language%20films%20release%20simultaneously%20this%20weekend%20in%20mainland%20China%20and%20will%20vie%20for%20a%20slice%20of%20the%20Lunar%20New%20Year%20holiday%20box%20office%20business.%20The%20week-long%20nationwide%20holiday%20period%20has%20in%20recent%20years%20become%20the%20most%20lucrative%20season%20for