t%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22830%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20wear%20decorated%20graduation%20caps%20during%20The%20Fashion%20Institute%20of%20Technology's%202017%20Commencement%20Ceremony%20at%20Arthur%20Ashe%20Stadium%20on%20May%2025%2C%202017%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c351a16fcb546d2d4ce13f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22554%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20CEO%20said%20creative%20thinkers%20with%20humanities%20backgrounds%20can%20help%20%26quot%3Bconnect%20the%20dots%26quot%3B%20for%20AI%20tech.%3Cp%3EDia%20Dipasupil%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBarth%C3%A9l%C3%A9my%20Kiss%2C%2036%2C%20is%20a%20politics%20graduate%20running%20his%20second%20AI%20company%20Powder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20creative%20thinkers%20from%20humanities%20backgrounds%20are%20necessary%20to%20push%20AI%20forward.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKiss%20has%20hired%20career%20switchers%20and%20liberal%20arts%20grads%20to%20work%20on%20his%20most%20recent%20AI%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Barth%C3%A9l%C3%A9my%20Kiss%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20AI%20entrepreneur%20in%20Paris.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20into%20AI%20started%20in%202015%20when%20I%20co-organized%20the%20%26quot%3BHello%20Tomorrow%26quot%3B%20startup%20conference%20in%20Paris.%20I%20heard%20a%20pitch%20that%20blew%20me%20away.%20Eric%20Risser%2C%20my%20future%20cofounder%20at%20Artomatix%2C%20was%20presenting%20an%20AI%20image-generation%20technique.%20This%20depiction%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20%E2%80%94%20still%20a%20developing%20field%20back%20then%20%E2%80%94%20showed%20computers%20mimicking%20and%20augmenting%20human%20creativity.%20I%20was%20so%20excited%20and%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20participate%20in%20this%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20building%20Artomatix%2C%20which%20was%20acquired%20by%20Unity%20in%202020%2C%20I%20co-founded%20Powder%20in%202018%2C%20my%20second%20startup%20in%20the%20AI%20space.%20We've%20created%20a%20PC%20app%20using%20half%20a%20dozen%20AI%20approaches%20to%20help%20edit%20long%20videos%20for%20video%20game%20streamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20this%20startup%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20people%20with%20a%20liberal%20arts%20background%20have%20a%20major%20edge%20in%20our%20industry.%20The%20liberal%20arts%20grads%20we've%20hired%20have%20a%20creative%2C%20human-centric%20approach%20to%20understanding%20the%20best%20applications%20of%20AI%20in%20their%20respective%20fields.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20a%20hunger%20for%20constant%20education%20and%20a%20desire%20for%20self-improvement%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20in%20this%20space.%20At%20a%20core%20level%2C%20liberal%20arts%20disciplines%20hone%20critical%20thinking.%20We%20need%20critical%20thinkers%20to%20challenge%20the%20results%20of%20AI.%20Models%20can%20hallucinate%2C%20so%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20cross-reference%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20need%20creative%20thinkers%20to%20get%20the%20best%20out%20of%20AI%20technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuman%20creativity%20is%20crucial%20in%20the%20AI%20space.%20AI%20models%20still%20require%20huge%20data%20sets%20to%20come%20up%20with%20creative%20solutions%20and%20don't%20adapt%20their%20learnings%20as%20dynamically%20as%20humans.%20Humans%20definitely%20have%20the%20upper%20hand%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20creativity%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20there%20was%20lots%20of%20excitement%20about%20foundational%20models%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20Midjourney%2C%20and%20Runway.%20We're%20only%20just%20scratching%20the%20surface%20of%20what%20this%20trend%20will%20bring.%20Creative%20people%20can%20connect%20the%20dots%20in%20unexpected%20ways%20to%20harness%20this%20new%20technology%20in%20the%20most%20convincing%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20hiring%2C%20we're%20looking%20for%20passion%20about%20what%20we%20do%20and%20a%20skillset%20in%20the%20intersection%20between%20gaming%2C%20video%20content%2C%20and%20AI.%20Candidates%20don't%20need%20to%20have%20AI%20experience.%20Even%20within%20our%20most%20technical%20research%20team%2C%20two%20members%20previously%20worked%20on%20topics%20adjacent%20to%20AI%2C%20but%20not%20strictly%20AI%2C%20like%20data%20engineering%20and%20content%20labeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECareer%20switchers%20and%20arts%20grads%20have%20a%20home%20in%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20Powder's%20staff%20are%20taking%20a%20new%20direction%20in%20their%20career%20when%20they%20start%2C%20simply%20because%20an%20application%20that%20harnesses%20AI%20is%20so%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20career%20switchers%20have%20a%20home%20in%20AI-related%20companies.%20We%20have%20a%20former%20creative%20in%20the%20ad%20industry%20who's%20now%20a%20UX%20designer%2C%20somebody%20else%20who%20was%20a%20trained%20architect%20and%20is%20now%20our%20front-end%20developer%2C%20and%20a%20former%20movie%20director%20who%20became%20a%20YouTuber%20and%20later%20our%20social-media%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20embrace%20career%20changes%2C%20it%20shows%20they're%20risk-takers.%20These%20kinds%20of%20employees%20will%20thrive%20provided%20their%20company%20supports%20them%20to%20learn%20and%20develop%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20political%20sciences%2C%20and%20my%20cofounder%20Stan%20is%20a%20fine%20art%20graduate%20who%20also%20studied%20moviemaking.%20He%20created%20our%20prototype%20and%20has%20always%20seen%20product%20design%20artistically.%20Our%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20Maryan%2C%20studied%20literature%20and%20macroeconomy%20before%20progressively%20moving%20into%20AI.%20His%20love%20for%20writing%20and%20economics%20helped%20him%20learn%20to%20become%20a%20great%20code%20writer.%20He%20says%20code%20is%20like%20literature%3A%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20written%20well%20and%20easily%20understood%20by%20anyone%20who%20reads%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20companies%20in%20the%20AI%20industry%20are%20staffed%20by%20creatives.%20Pierre%20Boulez%2C%20a%20composer%2C%20created%20the%20French%20AI%20music%20and%20sound%20company%20Ircam%20Lab.%20Many%20of%20its%20contributors%20and%20AI%20engineers%20are%20musicians.%20They%20have%20a%20creative%20foundation%20yet%20also%20want%20to%20solve%20problems%20with%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20in%20AI%20means%20learning%20on%20the%20job%2C%20no%20matter%20your%20background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20joining%20the%20company%2C%20it's%20a%20steep%20learning%20curve.%20Most%20personal%20and%20professional%20development%20happens%20through%20on-the-job%20training.%20We%20encourage%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20at%20work%20because%20we're%20developing%20an%20AI%20application.%20Our%20team%20needs%20to%20know%20the%20codes%20and%20standards%20in%20this%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tell%20our%20team%20they%20can%20subscribe%20to%20AI%20services%20to%20augment%20their%20work%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20enforce%20it.%20Adoption%20should%20be%20organic%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20personal%20desire%20to%20experiment.%20This%20new%20breed%20of%20application%20is%20so%20young%20that%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20it%2C%20we%20all%20need%20to%20be%20learning%20constantly%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20how%20long%20we%20have%20been%20at%20the%20company%20or%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20engineers%20are%20absolutely%20key%2C%20it's%20only%20through%20alliances%20between%20talent%20from%20liberal%20arts%20backgrounds%2C%20who%20can%20think%20creatively%20about%20building%20applications%20around%20this%20tech%20stack%2C%20that%20the%20technology%20will%20reach%20its%20full%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-companies-hiring-liberal-arts-humanities-grads-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707299867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c24dd66fcb546d2d4c879e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-companies-hiring-liberal-arts-humanities-grads-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20serial%20AI%20entrepeneur%20shares%20why%20he%20hires%20liberal%20arts%20and%20humanities%20graduates%20for%20his%20AI%20startup.%20He%20said%20creative%20thinkers%20are%20crucial%20to%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Megan%20Carnegie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-companies-hiring-liberal-arts-humanities-grads-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20Bhatt%20wins%20the%20internet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707299822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107488306%2Cimgsize-34452.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Falia-bhatt-wins-the-internet-as-she-wishes-the-daughter-of-a-photographer%2Farticleshow%2F107488301.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107488301.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlia%20Bhatt%2C%20riding%20high%20on%20successive%20hits%2C%20won%20hearts%20with%20a%20thoughtful%20gesture.%20Spotted%20after%20a%20yoga%20session%2C%20she%20greeted%20a%20photographer's%20daughter%20on%20her%20birthday%2C%20captured%20in%20a%20viral%20video.%20Fans%20praised%20her%20humility%20online.%20Amidst%20work%20commitments%2C%20she%20gears%20up%20for%20upcoming%20projects%20with%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20and%20Vicky%20Kaushal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%