E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20self-touted%20militia%20sniper%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20FBI%20and%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20sell%20an%20undercover%20agent%20an%20unregistered%20suppressor%20for%20an%20AK-47.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20more%20%E2%80%94%20the%20FBI%20says%20Paul%20Faye%20Sr.%20owned%20multiple%20weapons%20and%20explosives%20and%20was%20planning%20to%20launch%20a%20violent%20attack%20on%20people%20at%20the%20southern%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFaye%20was%20charged%20with%20the%20possession%20of%20an%20unregistered%20silencer%20under%20the%20National%20Firearms%20Act%2C%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24409164-paul-faye-sr-criminal-complaint-case-no-24-mj-1036%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriminal%20complaint%20%3C%2Fa%3Efiled%20on%20February%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20an%20undercover%20FBI%20agent%20contacted%20Faye%20via%20TikTok%2C%20after%20which%20the%20pair%20exchanged%20phone%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFaye%20subsequently%20told%20three%20undercover%20agents%20during%20a%20meeting%20in%20April%20that%20he%20believed%20the%20federal%20government%20was%20intentionally%20letting%20in%20illegal%20immigrants%20because%20it%20would%20benefit%20the%20authorities%2C%20per%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20one%20of%20the%20agents%20met%20Faye%20in%20December%2C%20Faye%20said%20he%20was%20coordinating%20with%20militia%20groups%20from%20Kentucky%2C%20Georgia%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20and%20Tennessee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFaye%20then%20told%20the%20agent%20that%20he%20planned%20to%20transport%20explosives%20to%20the%20border%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bstir%20up%20the%20hornet's%20nest%26quot%3B%20and%20trigger%20a%20%26quot%3Bdomino%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20be%20the%20first%20one%20on%20the%20scene%2C%20and%20the%20last%20one%20to%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20Faye%20said%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20addin