smisses-russian-oligarch-usmanovs-appeal-against-sanctions-latest-news%2Famp_articleshow%2F107486648.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feu-court-dismisses-russian-oligarch-usmanovs-appeal-against-sanctions-latest-news%2Famp_articleshow%2F107486648.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Mirage%20of%20%E2%80%98Nari%20Shakti%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Lakhpati%20Didi%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30153449%2FACF098D3-6123-4B67-A2E4-DCA712B4.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20budget%20speech%2C%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20has%20identified%20the%20unleashing%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Enari%20shakti%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(women%E2%80%99s%20power)%C2%A0%20as%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20achievements%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20since%20it%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014.%20She%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20empowerment%20of%20women%20through%20entrepreneurship%2C%20ease%20of%20living%20and%20dignity%20for%20them%20has%20gained%20momentum%20in%20these%20ten%20years%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20examples%20of%20this%20model%20of%20nari%20shakti%2C%20which%20has%20created%20a%20hype%20in%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20is%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20government%20has%20enabled%20the%20creation%20of%20one%20crore%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ELakhpati%20Didis%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20women%20whose%20household%20income%20is%20above%20one%20lakh%20per%20year%2C%20through%20self%20help%20groups%20(SHGs)%20under%20the%20Deendayal%20Antyodaya%20Yojna-National%20Rural%20Livelihoods%20Mission%20(DAY-NRLM).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20much%20hyped%20scheme%2C%20inaugurated%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20August%2015%2C%202023%2C%20aims%20at%20training%20women%20for%20the%20production%20of%20led%20bulbs%2C%20repairing%20and%20operation%20of%20drones%20for%20agriculture%2C%20plumbing%20and%20other%20non-traditional%20skills.%20The%20ministry%20in%20turn%20makes%20third%20party%20agreements%20and%20helps%20these%20women%20with%20branding%20and%20marketing%20their%20products.%20Some%20of%20the%20main%20partners%20of%20NRLM%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Rural%20Development%20are%20Patanjali%2C%20Flipkart%2C%20Bill%20and%20Melinda%20Gates%20Foundation%2C%20etc.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20ties%20women%20with%20credit%20lines%20and%20MUDRA%20loans%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20being%20serviced%20by%20the%20non-commercial%20banks%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20priority%20sector%20lending.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20intention%20to%20build%20links%20between%20agribusinesses%20and%20women%20is%20illustrated%20through%20the%20%E2%80%98Namo%20Drone%20Didi%E2%80%99%20programme%20that%20was%20announced%20in%20November%202023%20and%20has%20been%20allocated%20Rs%20500%20crore%20in%20the%20interim%20budget.%20This%20scheme%20is%20set%20to%20enrol%20women%20in%20the%20promotion%20of%20digital%20agriculture%20by%20providing%2015%2C000%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekisan%3C%2Fem%3E%20drones%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20they%20can%20rent%20out%20to%20farmers.%20In%20this%20sense%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20SHGs%20will%20become%20agents%20of%20corporate%20giants%20who%20aim%20to%20dominate%20the%20agricultural%20markets.%20It%20appears%20that%20programmes%20like%20%E2%80%98NAMO%20Drone%20Didi%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Lakhpati%20Didi%E2%80%99%20are%20being%20used%20to%20trap%20women%E2%80%99s%20SHGs%20into%20corporate%20networks%2C%20especially%20transnational%20agribusiness%20giants%20who%20are%20firm%20allies%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fbig-talk-small-action-modi-govts-work-on-womens-empowerment-in-the-last-9-years%5C%22%3EBig%20Talk%2C%20Small%20Action%3A%20Modi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Work%20on%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Empowerment%20in%20the%20Last%209%20Years%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20interim%20budget%20is%20trying%20to%20sell%20the%20idea%20that%20women%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20become%20wealthy%2C%20the%20government%20has%20squarely%20ignored%20their%20basic%20needs.%20By%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%98outcomes%E2%80%99%20not%20outlays%20are%20important%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20has%20absolved%20the%20government%20of%20all%20responsibility%20for%20providing%20women%20basic%20services.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHence%2C%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20while%20lofty%20claims%20are%20made%20about%20allocations%20and%20achievements%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20record%20on%20expenditure%20of%20these%20schemes%20is%20absolutely%20abysmal.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20has%20linked%20women%E2%80%99s%20dignity%20to%20the%20joint%20ownership%20of%20houses%20under%20the%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%20(Rural).%20However%2C%20the%20budget%20of%20the%20scheme%20shows%20that%20revised%20estimate%20for%20the%20scheme%20in%202023-24%20was%20about%2050%25%20of%20the%20budget%20estimate%2C%20implying%20that%20very%20little%20money%20was%20spent%20for%20the%20programme.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20the%20Har%20Ghar%20Jal%20programme%2C%20which%20has%20been%20marketed%20as%20pro-woman%2C%20the%20actual%20government%20expenditure%20in%202022-23%20was%2016%25%20lower%20than%20the%20previous%20year.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20budgetary%20estimate%20for%202024-25%20is%20even%20lower.%20The%20utilisation%20of%20funds%20in%20the%20flagship%20Swachch%20Bharat%20Mission%20(Gramin)%20for%20open%20defecation%20free%20villages%20remains%20at%2060-70%25%2C%20even%20if%20the%20outlays%20remain%20the%20same%20in%20each%20year.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESchemes%20and%20subsidies%20that%20are%20essential%20for%20wellbeing%20of%20women%20are%20seeing%20low%20government%20spending%20and%20allocation%20cutbacks.%20Some%20examples%20of%20these%20are%20nutrition%20(food%20subsidy%20and%20PM%20POSHAN)%2C%20education%20(scholarships)%2C%20widow%20pension%2C%20and%20employment%20(MGNREGA).%20The%20onus%20for%20these%20is%20slowly%20being%20shifted%20on%20the%20state%20governments%20without%20adequate%20support%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%20In%20short%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20shrugged%20off%20its%20responsibility%20for%20providing%20conducive%20living%20conditions%20for%20women%20in%20the%20country.%20Instead%2C%20it%20is%20arguing%20that%20women%20are%20responsible%20for%20their%20own%20%E2%80%98empowerment%E2%80%99%20by%20enhancing%20their%20capabilities%20and%20should%20fund%20their%20own%20development%20through%20their%20savings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fsohini-chattopadhyay-the-day-i-became-a-runner-book-review%5C%22%3ECan%20the%20Indian%20Sportswoman%20Speak%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20individualised%20notion%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%20has%20led%20to%20a%20neglect%20of%20the%20systemic%20discrimination%20and%20violence%20that%20has%20been%20faced%20by%20women%2C%20and%20this%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20interim%20budget.%20The%20proportion%20of%20the%20gender%20budget%20in%20total%20budgetary%20spending%20has%20remained%20at%20about%205-6%25%20during%20the%20two%20tenures%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20The%20money%20allocated%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20has%20remained%20at%20around%200.5%25%C2%A0%20of%20the%20total%20budgetary%20expenditure.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20rising%20violence%20against%20women%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20invest%20in%20infrastructure%20for%20support%20to%20victims%20is%20also%20questionable.%20The%20funds%20for%20Mission%20Shakti%2C%20combining%20schemes%20for%20protection%20and%20empowerment%20of%20women%2C%20are%20not%20even%200.1%25%20of%20the%20total%20budgetary%20expenditure%20and%2070%25%20of%20the%20Nirbhaya%20fund%20remains%20unspent.%20The%20lack%20of%20political%20will%20for%20augmenting%20infrastructure%20for%20protection%20of%20women%20has%20resulted%20in%20weak%20and%20tardy%20implementation%20of%20legislations%20against%20domestic%20violence%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20pattern%20is%20compatible%20with%20the%20continuous%20targeting%20and%20moral%20policing%20of%20women%20by%20the%20hindutva%20brigade.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pro-corporate%20and%20neoliberal%20policies%20of%20the%20government%20have%20created%20the%20conditions%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20this%20right-wing%20ideology.%20In%20this%20situation%2C%20the%20image%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Lakhpati%20Didi%E2%80%99%20is%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20hegemonic%20project%20of%20%E2%80%98Vikasit%20Bharat%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20being%20used%20to%20legitimate%20an%20authoritarian%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20weaken%20the%20resistance%20of%20the%20democratic%20women%E2%80%99s%20movement%20and%20fracture%20its%20social%20base.%20The%20women%20of%20India%20need%20to%20intensify%20their%20resistance%20and%20demystify%20the%20mirage%20of%20nari%20shakti%20and%20work%20towards%20ousting%20this%20%3Cem%3Emanuwadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EArchana%20Prasad%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707297353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30153449%2FACF098D3-6123-4B67-A2E4-DCA712B4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwom