0nor%20launches'%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707296470000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107485903%2Cimgsize-872532.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-targets-congress-predicts-they-wont-win-more-than-40-seats%2Farticleshow%2F107485947.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Congress%20and%20called%20it%20'outdated'.%20Takes%20a%20dig%20at%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20long%20speech%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Uses%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20remarks%20to%20challenge%20Congress.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20letter%20to%20the%20chief%20ministers%20and%20accused%20Congress%20of%20promoting%20colonial%20mindset.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-targets-congress-predicts-they-wont-win-more-than-40-seats%2Farticleshow%2F107485947.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%3A%20UN%20Warns%20of%20Israeli%20War%20Crimes%20as%20Rafah%20Ground%20Invasion%20Looms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160252%2FGA6xi9-WoAEKSsS.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20move%20by%20Israel%20to%20extend%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20into%20the%20massively%20overcrowded%20southern%20city%20of%20Rafah%20could%20lead%20to%20war%20crimes%20which%20must%20be%20prevented%20at%20all%20costs%2C%20the%20UN%20aid%20coordination%20office%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unocha.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%20xml%3Alang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EOCHA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20as%20the%20UN%20and%20Member%20States%20of%20the%20UN%2C%20can%20bear%20witness%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unocha.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOCHA%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0spokesperson%20Jens%20Laerke%20told%20journalists%20in%20Geneva.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20make%20clear%20what%20the%20law%20says%3A%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20indiscriminate%20bombing%20of%20densely%20populated%20areas%20may%20amount%20to%20war%20crimes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20came%20as%20OCHA%20reported%20an%20%E2%80%9Cincrease%20in%20strikes%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Rafah%20governorate%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Monday.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20thousands%20of%20Gazans%20continue%20to%20flood%20into%20Rafah%2C%20including%20many%20who%20have%20fled%20intense%20fighting%20in%20Khan%20Younis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20of%20this%20exodus%20is%20that%20Rafah%E2%80%99s%20population%20has%20increased%20five-fold%20since%20war%20erupted%20in%20the%20enclave%20on%20October%207%20in%20response%20to%20Hamas-led%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20that%20left%20some%201%2C200%20dead%20and%20more%20than%20250%20captured%20as%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20clear%2C%20intensified%20hostilities%20in%20Rafah%20in%20this%20situation%20could%20lead%20to%20large-scale%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%2C%20and%20we%20must%20do%20everything%20possible%20within%20our%20power%20to%20avoid%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr.%20Laerke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKhan%20Younis%20evacuation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfirming%20accounts%20of%20ongoing%20heavy%20fighting%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20Tommaso%20Della%20Longa%20from%20the%20International%20Federation%20of%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Red%20Crescent%20Societies%20(IFRC)%20reported%20that%C2%A08%2C000%20Gazans%20who%20had%20been%20sheltering%20at%C2%A0Al%20Amal%20Hospital%C2%A0had%20left%20the%20facility%20on%20Monday%C2%A0after%20Israeli%20authorities%20guaranteed%20safe%20passage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20positive%20development%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20is%20%E2%80%9Cbeyond%20catastrophic%E2%80%A6a%20nightmare%E2%80%9D%20that%20continues%20to%20get%20worse%2C%20the%20IFRC%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20as%20he%20mourned%20the%20death%20of%20aid%20worker%2C%20Hedaya%20Hamad%2C%20from%20the%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20Society%20(PRCS)%2C%20killed%20during%20shelling%20at%20Al%20Amal%20Hospital%20compound%20last%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%2C%20the%20hospital%20was%20surrounded%20by%20heavy%20shelling%2C%20fighting%2C%20no%20way%20in%2C%20no%20way%20out%2C%20(it%20was)%20hit%20several%20times%20and%20the%20last%20time%20was%20last%20Friday%20when%20this%20colleague%20was%20killed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr.%20Della%20Longa%20said%2C%20describing%20desperate%20shortages%20of%20medicine%2C%20food%20and%20water%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Calmost%20impossible%E2%80%9D%20task%20of%20replenishing%20stocks%20and%20of%20gaining%20access%20for%20ambulances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20100%20people%20remain%20inside%20the%20ailing%20health%20facility%2C%20including%20staff%20and%20volunteers%20as%20well%20as%20elderly%20patients%20and%20others%20with%20disabilities%20who%20could%20not%20be%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20even%20to%20think%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20whether%20Al%20Amal%20will%20close%20in%20the%20next%20coming%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20IFRC%20spokesperson%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20same%20scenario%20had%20played%20out%20at%20another%20hospital%2C%20Al%20Quds%2C%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20which%20the%20PCRS%20declared%20closed%20on%20November%2012.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20reality%20is%20that%20if%20the%20situation%20does%20not%20change%2C%20it%20will%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20continue%20the%20activities%20in%20the%20hospital.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http