sion-at-least-eight-killed-in-blast-outside-political-partys-office-13062733%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20Secretary-General%20Appoints%20Independent%20Panel%20to%20Examine%20UNRWA's%20Operations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07123556%2FGFp2Hp1WoAA3117.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20has%20appointed%20an%20independent%20panel%20to%20examine%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20(UNRWA)%2C%20in%20response%20to%20allegations%20linking%2012%20UNRWA%20personnel%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20against%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNRWA%20has%20more%20than%2013%2C000%20staff%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20was%20set%20up%20in%20consultation%20with%20UNRWA%20Commissioner-General%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%20and%20will%20be%20led%20by%20former%20French%20foreign%20minister%20Catherine%20Colonna%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146207%5C%22%3EUN%20News%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20will%20begin%20working%20from%20February%2014%20and%20an%20interim%20report%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20submitted%20to%20Guterres%20in%20late%20March.%20The%20final%20report%2C%20which%20will%20be%20made%20public%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20late%20April%2C%20according%20to%20UN%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Office%20of%20Internal%20Oversight%20Services%20is%20already%20probing%20the%20allegations%20that%2012%20UNRWA%20personnel%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20and%20the%20independent%20panel%E2%80%99s%20probe%20will%20in%20parallel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Israel%20accused%20UNRWA%20staff%20of%20being%20involved%20with%20Hamas%2C%20nine%20Western%20countries%20withdrew%20their%20funding%20for%20the%20agency.%20Given%20the%20scale%20of%20destruction%20in%20Gaza%20due%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20attacks%20which%20it%20claims%20are%20%E2%80%98retaliation%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20and%20which%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20is%20probing%20on%20grounds%20of%20%E2%80%98genocide%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20relief%20work%20has%20been%20viewed%20as%20providing%20essential%20humanitarian%20relief.%20Lazzarini%20had%20said%20this%20funding%20suspension%20is%20%E2%80%9Cshocking%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20lives%20of%20people%20in%20Gaza%20depends%20on%20this%20support%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channel4.com%2Fnews%2Fisraels-evidence-of-unrwa-hamas-allegations-examined%5C%22%3EChannel%204%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20British%20public%20broadcaster%2C%20has%20raised%20questions%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20dossier%20against%20UNRWA%20personnel%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20just%20six%20pages%20long%20and%20%E2%80%9Cprovides%20no%20evidence%20to%20support%20its%20explosive%20new%20claim%20that%20UNRWA%20staff%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fe326a1d3-7b45-4609-8179-dfb6a66abae9%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Time%3C%2Fem%3Es%3C%2Fa%3E%20too%20raised%20similar%20questions%20in%20a%20report%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20intelligence%20assessment%2C%20which%20has%20been%20seen%20by%20the%20FT%2C%20provides%20no%20evidence%20for%20the%20claims%2C%20which%20it%20says%20are%20based%20on%20smartphone%20intercepts%20and%20captured%20identity%20cards.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20accusations%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20UNRWA%2C%20the%20largest%20UN%20organisation%20in%20the%20region%2C%20is%20working%20under%20extremely%20challenging%20conditions%20to%20deliver%20lifesaving%20assistance%20to%20the%20two%20million%20people%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20who%20depend%20on%20it%20for%20their%20survival%20amidst%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20complex%20humanitarian%20crises%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guterres%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20since%20Israel%20had%20made%20these%20accusations%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20cooperation%20would%20be%20required%20during%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNRWA%20has%20been%20highlighting%20the%20scale%20of%20devastation%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20including%20the%20destruction%20of%20its%20own%20health%20centres.%20In%20a%20video%20posted%20to%20X%20recently%2C%20the%20agency%20highlighted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20nothing%20left%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20north%20of%20the%20strip%2C%20UNRWA%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20scale%20of%20destruction%20and%20loss%20is%20staggering%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20north%F0%9F%93%8D%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGazaStrip%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23GazaStrip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20destruction%20and%20loss%20is%20staggering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20footage%20shows%20one%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNRWA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%20health%20centres.%20There%20is%20nothing%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20unprecedented%20level%20of%20destruction%20and%20forced%20displacement%2C%20taking%20place%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fz1el0QfhEe%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fz1el0QfhEe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UNRWA%20(%40UNRWA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNRWA%2Fstatus%2F1754530324783239532%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20has%20said%20that%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20wounded%20or%20are%20missing%20in%20Gaza%20since