hhars%20is%20that%20ICICI%20Bank%20had%20sanctioned%20credit%20facilities%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%203%2C250%20crore%20to%20Videocon%20Group%20companies%2C%20promoted%20by%20Dhoot%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Banking%20Regulation%20Act%2C%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20guidelines%2C%20and%20credit%20policy%20of%20the%20private%20sector%20lender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20in%202019%2C%20the%20CBI%20named%20Chanda%20Kochhar%2C%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20and%20Dhoot%20along%20with%20Nupower%20Renewables%20(NRL)%2C%20managed%20by%20Deepak%20Kochhar%2C%20Supreme%20Energy%2C%20Videocon%20International%20Electronics%20Ltd%20and%20Videocon%20Industries%20Ltd%20as%20accused.%20The%20FIR%20was%20filed%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20sections%20related%20to%20criminal%20conspiracy%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20also%20alleged%20that%20in%20an%20act%20of%20%3Cem%3Equid%20pro%20quo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dhoot%20made%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2064%20crore%20in%20Nupower%20Renewables%20through%20Supreme%20Energy%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(SEPL)%2C%20and%20transferred%20SEPL%20to%20Pinnacle%20Energy%20Trust%20managed%20by%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20through%20a%20circuitous%20route%20between%202010%20and%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707291048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07120934%2FEffect-2024-02-07T120925.773.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fvideocon-icici-bank-loan-case-bombay-hc-declares-arrest-of-chanda-kochhar-husband-illegal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Anuja%20Prabhudessai%20and%20Justice%20N.R.%20Borkar%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20February%206%2C%20upheld%20a%20previous%20order%20by%20the%20same%20court%20but%20by%20a%20different%20bench%2C%20granting%20them%20bail%20in%20January%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canon