Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20expects%20that%20the%20State%20will%20endeavour%20to%20pay%20the%20balance%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20to%20all%20similarly%20placed%20persons%20instead%20of%20forcing%20the%20family%20members%20of%20persons%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20manual%20scavenging%20to%20approach%20this%20Court%20by%20filing%20writ%20petitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Subramonium%20Prasad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%2C%20widows%20who%20lost%20their%20husbands%20because%20of%20the%20dangerous%2C%20outlawed%2C%20caste-based%20practice%2C%20said%20they%20had%20received%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20from%20the%20Delhi%20government%20so%20far.%20The%20high%20court%20held%20that%20given%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20these%20families%20were%20entitled%20to%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanual-scavenging-sc-hikes-compensation-to-rs-30-lakh-orders-govt-to-ensure-complete-ban%5C%22%3E%20had%20raised%20the%20compensation%20amount%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20cases%20of%20sewer%20deaths%20from%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20victim%20to%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%20The%20court%20had%20also%20said%20compensation%20amount%20in%20the%20case%20of%20permanent%20disability%20should%20be%20made%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20be%20given%20for%20other%20forms%20of%20disability.%20Any%20victims%20who%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20received%20this%20amount%20so%20far%20should%20be%20given%20it%2C%20the%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManual%20scavenging%20is%20an%20outlawed%20practice%20under%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20(PEMSR)%20Act%2C%202013.%20The%20Act%20bans%20the%20use%20of%20any%20individual%20for%20manually%20cleaning%2C%20carrying%2C%20disposing%20of%2C%20or%20otherwise%20handling%2C%20in%20any%20manner%2C%20human%20excreta%20till%20its%20disposal.%20However%2C%20even%20ten%20years%20later%2C%20this%20law%20has%20not%20meant%20that%20the%20practice%20stops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F339-lives-lost-to-manual-scavenging-in-the-last-five-years-govt-data-reveals%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Union%20social%20justice%20and%20empowerment%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20339%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20while%20cleaning%20sewers%20and%20septic%20tanks%20in%20India%20between%202018%20and%202023.%20As%20per%20the%20data%20presented%20before%20the%20parliament%20by%20the%20government%2C%C2%A0nine%20such%20deaths%20were%20recorded%20in%202023%2C%2066%20in%202022%2C%2058%20in%202021%2C%2022%20in%202020%2C%20117%20in%202019%2C%20and%2067%20deaths%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707287436000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F25203601%2Fdelhi-hc.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fhc-tells-delhi-govt-to-follow-sc-orders-pay-rs-30-lakh-compensation-for-all-manual-scavenging-deaths%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20petitioners%2C%20widows%20who%20lost%20their%20husbands%20because%20of%20the%20dangerous%20outlawed%20practice%2C%20said%20they%20had%20received%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20from%20the%20Delhi%20government%20so%20far.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fhc-tells-delhi-govt-to-follow-sc-orders-pay-rs-30-lakh-compensation-for-all-manual-scavenging-deaths%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UGC's%20Committee%20to%20Probe%20Caste%20Discrimination%20on%20Campuses%20Offers%20No%20Solutions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07094053%2FVemula-Tadvi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20response%20to%20a%20five-year-old%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20filed%20by%20two%20mothers%20who%20lost%20their%20children%20to%20alleged%20institutionalised%20caste%20discrimination%2C%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20had%20set%20up%20a%20nine-member%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%20But%20the%20committee%20appears%20to%20have%20more%20problems%20than%20solutions%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbeda%20Tadvi%20and%20Radhika%20Vemula%20filed%20the%20petition%20seeking%20accountability%20and%20adequate%20mechanisms%20to%20deal%20with%20caste-based%20discrimination%20in%20university%20spaces.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%20matter%20in%20July%20last%20year%2C%20had%20called%20the%20issue%20%E2%80%9Cserious%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csensitive%E2%80%9D.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20UGC%20set%20up%20a%20nine-member%20expert%20committee%20to%20revisit%20its%20regulations%20and%20schemes%20available%20for%20students%20belonging%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20other%20marginalised%20communities.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20committee%20has%20met%20at%20least%20three%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20is%20chaired%20by%20Shailesh%20N.%20Zala%2C%20former%20vice%20chancellor%20of%20the%20Maharaja%20Krishnakumarsinhji%20Bhavnagar%20University.%20Going%20by%20the%20background%20of%20many%20of%20its%20members%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20members%20were%20not%20appointed%20for%20the%20work%20they%20have%20done%20in%20the%20academic%20space%20but%20for%20their%20political%20affiliations.%20Take%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Zala%E2%80%99s%20appointment.%20Before%20assuming%20his%20role%20as%20the%20MK%20Bhavnagar%20University%E2%80%99s%20vice-chancellor%2C%20Zala%20was%20the%20vice-president%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20the%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20RSS.%20He%20has%20remained%20consistent%20with%20his%20political%20affiliation.%20After%20his%20retirement%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahmedabadmirror.com%2Fex-vcs-with-saffron-party-links-selected-as-presiding-officers%2F81018671.html%5C%22%3Ea%20presiding%20officer%20for%20the%20Ahmedabad%20civic%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20member%2C%20Dr%20Vijay%20Shankar%20Mishra%2C%20the%20acting%20principal%20of%20Satyawati%20College%20(night%20college)%20in%20Delhi%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fsatyawati-evening-college-principal-sent-on-leave-over-administrative-irregularities%2Fstory-0kKeiYRHdX26JI5F2zxCEM.html%5C%22%3Eaccused%20of%20not%20following%20the%20reservation%20roster%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20college%20appointments.%20After%20the%20staff%20members%20employed%20under%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20quotas%20retired%2C%20Mishra%20would%20allegedly%20issue%20circulars%20but%20not%20mention%20that%20those%20were%20reserved%20seats.%20The%20UGC%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20take%20someone%20like%20Mishra%20on%20board%20even%20when%20he%20has%20allegations%20against%20him%20indicating%20caste%20discrimination%20raises%20serious%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20following%20complaints%20by%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20MLCs%20that%20many%20ST%20students%20availed%20reservation%20even%20after%20converting%20to%20Christianity%20or%20Islam%2C%20a%20three-member%20committee%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20This%20move%20was%20widely%20criticised%20and%20called%20out%20for%20its%20insensitivity%20towards%20the%20tribal%20community%20and%20politicisation%20of%20their%20choice%20to%20practice%20religion.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20committee%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20Dr%20Murlidhar%20Chandekar%2C%20the%20former%20vice%20chancellor%20of%20Sant%20Gadge%20Baba%20Amravati%20University%2C%20and%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20pro-BJP%20man.%20Now%20Chandekar%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20UGC%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20affidavit%20was%20filed%20by%20Prashant%20Dwivedi%2C%20deputy%20under%20secretary%20of%20the%20UGC%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20over%20700-page%20petition%20filed%20by%20Tadvi%20and%20Vemula.%20The%20petition%20filed%20in%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20through%20their%20lawyer%20Disha%20Wadekar%2C%20gives%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20UGCs%20inability%20to%20protect%20students%20from%20a%20toxic%20casteist%20atmosphere%20in%20university%20spaces.%20Indira%20Jaising%20is%20the%20senior%20counsel%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202016%2C%20Vemula%E2%80%99s%20son%20Rohith%20Vemula%2C%20a%20PhD%20scholar%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Hyderabad%20(UoH)%2C%20along%20with%20five%20other%20Dalit%20students%2C%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20university%20housing%20facility%20for%20an%20alleged%20attack%20on%20an%20ABVP%20member.%20As%20the%20expelled%20students%20intensified%20their%20protest%20against%20the%20university%20administration%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20a%20few%20days%20into%20the%20protest%2C%20on%20January%2017%2C%202016%2C%20Rohith%20ended%20his%20own%20life.%20UoH%20vice-chancellor%20Appa%20Rao%20Podile%2C%20then%20BJP%20MLC%20N.%20Ramachandra%20Rao%20and%20two%20ABVP%20members%20(Susheel%20Kumar%20and%20Rama%20Krishna)%20were%20accused%20of%20abetting%20Rohith%E2%80%99s%20suicide.%20An%20FIR%20was%20filed%20against%20them%2C%20but%20the%20police%20failed%20to%20take%20any%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Dr%20Payal%20Tadvi%E2%80%99s%20suicide%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fpayal-tadvi-suicide-note-receovered%5C%22%3Eher%20suicide%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20her%20mother%20Abeda%20Tadvi%E2%80%99s%20testimony%20have%20ensured%20that%20her%20three%20harassers%20%E2%80%93%20senior%20doctors%20Hema%20Ahuja%2C%20Bhakti%20Mehare%20and%20Ankita%20Khandelwal%20%E2%80%93%20were%20immediately%20arrested.%20A%20damning%201%2C200-page%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdr-payal-tadvi-suicide-chargesheet%5C%22%3Echargesheet%20was%20filed%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20them.%20They%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20torturing%20Payal%20for%20an%20entire%20year%20and%20hurling%20casteist%20slurs%20at%20her.%20Tadvis%20belong%20to%20the%20Bhil%20(of%20the%20Tadvi%20sub-caste)%20tribal%20community%2C%20and%20Payal%20was%20perhaps%20the%20first%20woman%20from%20her%20community%20to%20have%20become%20a%20doctor.%20Advovate%20Wadekar%20is%20representing%20Abeda%20Tadvi%20in%20the%20criminal%20proceedings%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fsupreme-court-abeda-tadvi-radhika-vemula%5C%22%3EWhy%20Payal%20Tadvi%20and%20Rohith%20Vemula%E2%80%99s%20Mothers%20Have%20Taken%20Their%20Fight%20to%20the%20SC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Rohith%20and%20Payal%E2%80%99s%20deaths%2C%20the%20petition%20also%20lists%20numerous%20other%20suicides%20that%20occurred%20in%20Indian%20universities%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%20While%20some%20of%20these%20deaths%20were%20covered%20in%20the%20media%2C%20many%20of%20them%20were%20covered%20in%20an%20independent%20study%20done%20by%20a%20Delhi-based%20organisation%20called%20the%20Insight%20Foundation%2C%20headed%20by%20Anoop%20Kumar.%20The%20foundation%20had%20studied%20these%20cases%20and%20documented%20the%20experiences%20of%20students%20who%20were%20pushed%20to%20kill%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20as%20cases%20of%20discrimination%20and%20suicides%20were%20on%20a%20rise%2C%20the%20UGC%20was%20compelled%20to%20notify%20the%20UGC%20(Promotion%20of%20Equity%20in%20Higher%20Educational%20Institutions)%20Regulations%202012%2C%20also%20called%20the%20Equity%20Regulations.%20These%20regulations%20required%20all%20colleges%2Funiversities%20to%20establish%20an%20Equal%20Opportunity%20Cell%20to%20oversee%20the%20promotion%20of%20equality%20in%20the%20institution%20and%20appoint%20an%20Anti-Discrimination%20Officer%20to%20investigate%20complaints%20regarding%20discrimination%20in%20breach%20of%20equity.%20Although%20the%20UGC%20introduced%20the%20Equity%20Regulations%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20address%20complaints%20of%20caste-based%20discrimination%20on%20campus%2C%20the%20regulations%20have%20not%20proven%20to%20be%20effective%20or%20sufficient%2C%20the%20petitioners%20point%20out.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20do%20not%20provide%20for%20an%20independent%20mechanism%20of%20grievance%20redressal%20since%20the%20Anti-Discrimination%20Officer%20under%20the%20regulations%20and%20the%20appellate%20authority%2C%20are%20the%20Professor%2FAssociate%20Professor%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20institution%20respectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20UGC%E2%80%99s%20affidavit%2C%20Dwivedi%20lists%20the%20same%20rules%20and%20regulations%20that%20the%20petitioners%20have%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cinadequate%E2%80%9D%20to%20tackle%20casteism%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20drawback%20of%20the%20Equity%20Regulations%20is%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20apply%20to%20faculty%20members%20and%20other%20employees%20belonging%20to%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities.%20The%20regulations%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20protect%20victims%20of%20discrimination%20from%20the%20hostile%20environment%20arising%20out%20of%20their%20complaints.%20The%20petition%20raises%20these%20issues%2C%20but%20the%20UGC%2C%20in%20its%20affidavit%2C%20has%20failed%20to%20offer%20any%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20cites%20rich%20data%20collated%20through%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20According%20to%C2%A0%20data%20revealed%20under%20the%20RTI%20request%20filed%20by%20Amnesty%20International%20India%2C%20in%202015-16%2C%20only%20155%20out%20of%20over%20800%20universities%20have%20submitted%20their%20Action%20Taken%20Reports%20(ATRs)%20to%20the%20UGC.%20Similarly%2C%20another%20RTI%20reveals%20that%20in%202017-18%2C%20only%20419%20out%20of%20the%20over%20800%20universities%20filed%20their%20ATRs.%20The%20UGC%20has%20merely%20collected%20their%20ATRs%20and%20not%20followed%20up%20with%20the%20universities%20failing%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20Equity%20Regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20collected%20from%20different%20universities%20also%20shows%20that%20many%20universities%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20mechanism%20till%20date%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20discrimination%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20perpetrators%20have%20been%20let%20off%20with%20just%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwarning%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707287429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07094053%2FVemula-Tadvi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fugcs-committee-to-probe-caste-discrimination-on-campuses-offers-no-solutions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Members%20of%20the%20committee%20have%20no%20track%20record%20of%20tackling%20discrimination%20%E2%80%93%20but%20do%20have%20a%20closeness%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Their%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20does%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20many%20issues%20raised%20in%20Abeda%20Tadvi%20and%20Radhika%20Vemula%E2%80%99s%20petition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fugcs-committee-to-probe-caste-discrimination-on-campuses-offers-no-solutions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vegetarian%20thali%20costlier%20in%20last%20one%20year%2C%20non-veg%20thali%20cheaper%3A%20CRISIL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707287312000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-01%2F08%2Ffull%2F1704736254-7365.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fvegetarian-thali-costlier-in-last-one-year-non-veg-thali-cheaper-crisil-124020700368_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rise%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20veg%20thali%20signals%20that%20the%20food%20inflation%