.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20election%20campaign%20in%20Pakistan%20concluded%20on%20Tuesday%20with%20an%20advisory%20from%20the%20country's%20election%20commission%2C%20instructing%20all%20political%20parties%20and%20candidates%20to%20cease%20electioneering%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls%20scheduled%20for%20Thursday%2C%20according%20to%20Dawn.%20On%20the%20final%20day%20of%20the%20campaign%2C%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20the%20Chairperson%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20People's%20Party%20(PPP)%2C%20visited%20Larkana%2C%20the%20historical%20stronghold%20of%20the%20Bhutto%20political%20dynasty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Felection-campaign-ends-in-pakistan-following-ecp-advisory%2Farticleshow%2F107477464.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Felection-campaign-ends-in-pakistan-following-ecp-advisory%2Famp_articleshow%2F107477464.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Felection-campaign-ends-in-pakistan-following-ecp-advisory%2Famp_articleshow%2F107477464.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Despite%20Opposition%20From%20Kuki-Zos%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Says%20India%20Will%20Fence%20Entire%20Northeast%20Border%20With%20Myanmar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07110016%2FRoad_Map.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20announced%20that%20the%20entire%201%2C643-km-long%20India-Myanmar%20border%2C%20along%20the%20states%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Manipur%20and%20Mizoram%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20will%20be%20fenced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAmitShah%2Fstatus%2F1754848035895398706%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%206%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20building%20impenetrable%20borders.%20It%20has%20decided%20to%20construct%20a%20fence%20along%20the%20entire%201%2C643-kilometer-long%20Indo-Myanmar%20border.%E2%80%9D%20A%20patrol%20track%20along%20the%20border%20would%20also%20be%20made%2C%20in%20order%20to%20facilitate%20better%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20will%20end%20the%20free%20movement%20regime%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20FMR)%20that%20was%20only%20formalised%20in%202018.%20The%20FMR%20lets%20people%20living%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%20enter%20up%20to%2016%20km%20of%20the%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20country%20without%20needing%20a%20visa.%20As%20they%20often%20come%20from%20the%20same%20ethnic%20group%2C%20they%20are%20allowed%20to%20stay%20up%20to%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20a%20step%20back%20from%20the%20Act%20East%20policy%2C%20and%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20ability%20to%20move%20freely%20across%20eastern%20borders%2C%20a%20practice%20in%20place%20since%20pre-independence%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20gave%20details%20of%20the%20entire%20fencing%20regime%20being%20planned%2C%20making%20the%20principle%20the%20same%20as%20what%20governs%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border.%20%E2%80%9COut%20of%20the%20total%20border%20length%2C%20a%2010km%20stretch%20in%20Moreh%2C%20Manipur%2C%20has%20already%20been%20fenced.%20Furthermore%2C%20two%20pilot%20projects%20of%20fencing%20through%20a%20Hybrid%20Surveillance%20System%20(HSS)%20are%20under%20execution.%20They%20will%20fence%20a%20stretch%20of%201km%20each%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Manipur.%20Additionally%2C%20fence%20works%20covering%20approx%2020km%20in%20Manipur%20have%20also%20been%20approved%2C%20and%20the%20work%20will%20start%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20minister%20had%20announced%20that%20India%20would%20fence%20the%20border%20along%20Myanmar%20to%20stop%20free%20movement%2C%20but%20what%20he%20announced%20yesterday%20spans%20a%20much%20wider%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20two%20chief%20ministers%20%E2%80%93%20one%2C%20the%20only%20non-NDA%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20recently%20elected%20chief%20minister%20Lalduhoma%2C%20and%20the%20other%20an%20NDA%20ally%2C%20Nagaland%20chief%20minister%20Neiphiu%20Rio%20%E2%80%93%20had%20spoken%20up%20against%20bids%20to%20fence%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalduhoma%20had%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Delhi%20last%20month%20and%20discussed%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20international%20border%20with%20Myanmar.%20Lalduhoma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funacceptable-mizoram-cm-to-pm-external-affairs-minister-on-fencing-indo-myanmar-border%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%20Union%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20fencing%20the%20Indo-Myanmar%20border%20will%20be%20%E2%80%9Cunacceptable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalduhoma%20told%20Jaishankar%20in%20a%20meeting%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20January%20%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20British%20had%20separated%20the%20Mizos%20by%20carving%20out%20Burma%20from%20India.%20They%20divided%20the%20Mizo%20ethnic%20people%E2%80%99s%20land%20from%20the%20ancient%20days%20into%20two%20parts.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20cannot%20accept%20the%20border%2C%20instead%20we%20always%20dream%20of%20becoming%20a%20nation%20under%20one%20administration.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20brought%20it%20up%20in%20his%20meeting%20with%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20particularly%20sore%20point%20with%20the%20Kuki-Zos%20of%20Manipur%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20and%20will%20cut%20deep%2C%20given%20ethnic%20ties%20and%20the%20marginalisation%20they%20have%20been%20particularly%20conscious%20of%20since%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20that%20has%20flared%20up%20and%20divided%20the%20state%20since%20over%20nine%20months%2C%20leaving%20over%20200%20dead%2C%20over%2067%2C000%20persons%20displaced%20and%20at%20least%20250%20churches%20destroyed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Findia-decides-to-fence-entire-border-with-myanmar%2Fcid%2F1998767%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Kuki-Zos%20%E2%80%9Chave%20opposed%20the%20move%20to%20fence%20the%20border%20because%20the%20Chins%20of%20Myanmar%20share%20the%20same%20Zo%20ancestry%20with%20the%20Mizos%20and%20the%20Kukis.%20The%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20blame%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20radical%20groups%20for%20the%20unrest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20all%20the%20mountains%20and%20rugged%20terrain%20along%20the%20border%2C%20it%20is%20next%20to%20impossible%20to%20fence%20the%20entire%20frontier.%20It%20is%20also%20going%20to%20destabilise%20the%20people-to-people%20contact%20that%20has%20existed%20for%20decades%20between%20the%20people%20in%20the%20border%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20intelligence%20bureau%20official%20was%20quoted%20as%20telling%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20underlining%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20establishment%20has%20been%20highlighting%20allegations%20that%20%E2%80%98undocumented%20immigrants%E2%80%99%20from%20Myanmar%20are%20behind%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20has%20engulfed%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20minister%20Shah%20alluded%20in%20his%20post%20that%20the%20fencing%20plan%20is%20to%20recommit%20the%20Modi%20government%20%E2%80%9Cto%20building%20impenetrable%20borders%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20that%20erupted%20with%20new%20tensions%20in%20Manipur%20last%20year%20may%20not%20experience%20any%20closure%20with%20this.%20The%20state%2C%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20who%20is%20seen%20as%20divisive%20by%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20tribal%20minority%2C%20could%20end%2