2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68224393.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68224393.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20Act%20as%20a%20Catalyst%20for%20Deeper%20Transformation%20in%20Our%20Democracy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F06183311%2FEffect-2024-02-06T183242.830.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFar%20away%20from%20the%20buzz%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20spectacle%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20another%20event%20has%20been%20making%20news.%20Starting%20January%2014%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20(BJNY)%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20at%20its%20helm%2C%20is%20traversing%20India%20from%20east%20to%20west%20(complementing%20his%20south-north%20yatra%20last%20year).%20A%20journey%20of%206%2C713%20km%2C%20undertaken%20mostly%20by%20bus%20will%20traverse%2016%20states%2C%20with%20its%20message%20of%20%3Cem%3Enyay%20%3C%2Fem%3E(justice)%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20events%20in%20Ayodhya%20symbolise%20the%20consolidation%20of%20authoritarian%2C%20communal%2C%20masculine%20power%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Can%20the%20BJNY%20be%20a%20counter%2C%20by%20promoting%20a%20vision%20of%20nyay%20that%20includes%20deeper%20notions%20and%20grounded%20notions%20of%20democracy%3F%20This%20question%20goes%20well%20beyond%20the%20immediate%20impact%20it%20may%20have%20on%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20not%20only%20because%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20mind-bending%20communication%20and%20financial%20clout%20but%20because%20we%20%3Cem%3Eneed%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20notion%20that%20democracy%20is%20about%20elections%20and%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJNY%20has%20three%20objectives%3A%20economic%20justice%20(a%20job%20for%20every%20Indian%20youth%2C%20and%20ending%20inequality)%3B%20social%20justice%20(participation%20of%20marginalised%20Indians%20in%20decision-making%2C%20unity%20and%20harmony)%3B%20and%20political%20justice%20(promoting%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20vision%2C%20the%20constitutional%20values%20of%20dignity%20and%20respect%20for%20all%20Indians).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20Indian%20context%2C%20these%20are%20crucial%20objectives.%20There%20is%20a%20serious%20crisis%20of%20livelihoods%20(according%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmie.com%2Fkommon%2Fbin%2Fsr.php%3Fkall%3Dwarticle%26dt%3D20240104181058%26msec%3D536%5C%22%3Eunemployment%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20grown%20from%205.5%25%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20to%209%25%20in%202023)%2C%20growing%20religious-ethnic%20hatred%20and%20conflict%2C%20brazen%20state%20attacks%20on%20democratic%20rights%20of%20peaceful%20dissent%2C%20infiltration%20or%20muzzling%20of%20independent%20institutions%20created%20to%20check%20misuse%20of%20power%20and%20money%20(constitutional%20bodies%2C%20media%2C%20universities)%2C%20open%20crony%20capitalism%20aided%20by%20weakening%20of%20labour%20and%20environmental%20laws%2C%20ecological%20collapse%20and%20climate%20crisis%20impacting%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20people%2C%20and%20disgusting%20state%20support%20to%20toxic%20masculinity%20and%20patriarchy%20(the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-her-own-words-what-bilkis-bano-went-through-in-2002%5C%22%3EBilkis%20Bano%3C%2Fa%3E%20case%20being%20one%20of%20many%20examples).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-theres-more-to-the-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-than-just-winning-elections%5C%22%3EWhy%20There%E2%80%99s%20More%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20Than%20Winning%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20symbolically%20just%20that%20the%20BJNY%20commenced%20in%20Manipur%2C%20given%20its%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%20and%20its%20shocking%20neglect%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20The%20Yatra%20appears%20to%20have%20touched%20a%20chord%20in%20north-east%20India%2C%20providing%20opportunities%20for%20those%20troubled%20by%20human%20rights%20and%20ecological%20violations%20to%20air%20their%20issues.%20Hopefully%2C%20it%20can%20continue%20to%20create%20such%20spaces%20of%20dialogue%20and%20hear%20people%E2%80%99s%20voices%20across%20its%20entire%20route%20to%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20indeed%20the%20BJNY%20has%20to%20catalyse%20deeper%20transformation%2C%20it%20has%20to%20go%20beyond%20considerations%20of%20immediate%20electoral%20gains%20and%20think%20instead%20of%20long-term%20goals%20of%20strengthening%20grounded%20democracy.%20Its%20leadership%20seems%20to%20be%20signalling%20this.%20But%20for%20this%20to%20happen%20meaningfully%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20connect%20to%20and%20support%20the%20myriad%20people%E2%80%99s%20actions%20of%20change%20scattered%20around%20the%20country.%20There%20are%20thousands%20of%20initiatives%20to%20create%20dignified%20livelihoods%20in%20agriculture%2C%20crafts%2C%20forestry%20and%20fisheries%2C%20small%20manufacturing%2C%20community-led%20tourism%2C%20open%20source%20technologies%2C%20eco-friendly%20construction%2C%20and%20much%20else.%20There%20are%20inspiring%20examples%20of%20regenerating%20and%20protecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20ecological%20base%2C%20respecting%20nature%20and%20wildlife%20while%20using%20this%20base%20for%20enhancing%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F06183711%2FGEIvTV3XkAAfRNi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F06183711%2FGEIvTV3XkAAfRNi.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F06183711%2FGEIvTV3XkAAfRNi-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F06183711%2FGEIvTV3XkAAfRNi-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695954%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20part%20of%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Assam.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40rahulgandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20successful%20struggles%20to%20achieve%20gender%20equality%2C%20gain%20respect%20for%20sexual%20minorities%2C%20secure%20access%20to%20those%20with%20disabilities%2C%20strengthen%20community%20health%20based%20on%20both%20traditional%20and%20modern%20medical%20systems%2C%20and%20create%20learning%20spaces%20that%20are%20enjoyable%2C%20creative%2C%20and%20enabling%20youth%20to%20enter%20into%20responsible%20adulthood%20rather%20than%20aspire%20to%20rat-race%20jobs%20that%20only%20sustain%20capitalist%20profits%20and%20state%20power.%20All%20of%20these%20signify%20that%20democracy%20is%20much%20less%20about%20taking%20over%20power%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20much%20more%20about%20enabling%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20most%20marginalised%20in%20all%20decisions%20affecting%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recently%20released%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fover-85-movements-unite-under-vikalp-sangam-in-peoples-manifesto-for-a-just-equitable-and-sustainable-india%2Farticle67706526.ece%5C%22%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Manifesto%20for%20a%20Just%2C%20Equitable%2C%20and%20Sustainable%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%2085%20national%20movements%20and%20organisations%20have%20spelt%20out%20an%20agenda%20that%20builds%20on%20such%20grounded%20initiatives.%20It%20lays%20out%20actions%20%E2%80%93%20practical%20and%20policy%20level%20%E2%80%93%20that%20could%20take%20India%20towards%20the%20goals%20that%20the%20BJNY%20has%20listed%2C%20as%20also%20the%20goals%20of%20ecological%20and%20cultural%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrankly%2C%20I%20have%20little%20hope%20of%20any%20political%20party%20picking%20up%20such%20a%20long-term%20vision%2C%20much%20less%20trying%20to%20achieve%20it%20even%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%20When%20in%20government%2C%20the%20Congress%20promoted%20fundamentally%20contradictory%20policies.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20economic%20%E2%80%98reforms%E2%80%99%20in%201991%20hastened%20India%E2%80%99s%20slide%20down%20the%20pathway%20of%20ecological%20collapse%20and%20institutionalised%20worker%20insecurity%20(sustaining%20or%20exacerbating%20over%2090%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20remaining%20unorganised%20or%20informal).%20On%20the%20other%2C%20in%20a%20few%20years%20of%20enlightened%20policy-making%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20it%20brought%20in%20a%20series%20of%20rights-based%20legislations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201990s%20it%20had%20brought%20in%20progressive%20constitutional%20amendments%20towards%20rural%20and%20urban%20self-governance%2C%20but%20its%20own%20governments%20did%20little%20to%20implement%20them.%20Its%20record%20in%20maintaining%20India%E2%80%99s%20unique%20vision%20of%20secularism%2C%20respecting%20all%20religions%20and%20faiths%20equally%2C%20is%20also%20mixed%20(who%20can%20forget%20the%20anti-Sikh%20riots%20after%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%3F).%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20unique%20contribution%20is%20that%20it%20is%20abandoning%20all%20the%20progressive%20elements%20of%20the%20Congress%20heritage%20while%20intensifying%20the%20regressive%20ones%20(and%20bringing%20in%20some%20of%20its%20own%2C%20to%20boot).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20some%20of%20BJNY%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20are%20thinking%20beyond%20neoliberal%20economics%20and%20short-term%20electoral%20gains%2C%20they%20can%20still%20contribute%20to%20long-term%20positive%20transformation%2C%20including%20through%20progressive%20policies%20where%20they%20are%20in%20government.%20But%20for%20this%2C%20they%20need%20to%20forge%20a%20continuing%2C%20respectful%20relationship%20with%20mass%20movements%20and%20community%20initiatives%20of%20the%20kind%20described%20above.%20They%20need%20to%20adopt%20and%20help%20achieve%20the%20slogan%20emanating%20from%20Adivasi%20villages%20in%20Gadchiroli%20(Maharashtra)%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20elect%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20but%20in%20our%20village%2C%20we%20%3Cem%3Eare%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20government%E2%80%9D.%20Or%20the%20message%20of%20Dalit%20women%20farmers%20of%20Zaheerabad%20(Telangana)%3A%20%E2%80%9CSeeds%20and%20land%20are%20ours%2C%20food%20is%20our%20sovereign%20right%2C%20not%20for%20profit-making%20by%20corporations%20and%20governments%E2%80%9D.%20Or%20what%20young%20weavers%20in%20Kachchh%20are%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20%3Cem%3Emake%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20why%20do%20you%20need%20multinational%20corporations%20to%20come%2C%20they%20only%20displace%20us%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJNY%20anthem%20says%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHam%20pahunchenge%20har%20ghar%20tak%2C%20Nyay%20ka%20haque%20milne%20tak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(we%20will%20reach%20every%20house%2C%20till%20the%20right%20to%20justice%20is%20achieved)%E2%80%9D.%20Achieving%20this%20needs%20fundamental%20transformations%20in%20politics%20towards%20true%20people-based%20swaraj%2C%20economics%20that%20centre%20life%20in%20all%20its%20forms%2C%20and%20a%20society%20where%20everyone%20can%20flourish%20without%20discrimination.%20Political%20parties%20bent%20on%20winning%20elections%20and%20staying%20in%20power%20are%20not%20cut%20out%20to%20achieve%20these%2C%20nor%20is%20a%20democracy%20centred%20around%20hostile%20elections%20and%20the%20power%20of%20elected%20representatives.%20But%20politicians%20with%20a%20deeper%20vision%20of%20swaraj%2C%20entailing%20visions%20and%20strategies%20well%20beyond%20a%20five-year%20electoral%20cycle%2C%20can%20help%20communities%20on%20the%20ground%20achieve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20was%20assassinated%2C%20Gandhiji%20had%20urged%20the%20Congress%20Party%20cadre%20to%20spread%20out%20across%20the%20country%20to%20enable%20grounded%20swaraj%2C%C2%A0%20rather%20than%20crave%20only%20for%20ruling%20from%20New%20Delhi.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20vision%20BJNY%20can%20promote%2C%20it%20may%20be%20able%20to%20contribute%20to%20%3Cem%3Enyay%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20its%20holistic%20sense.%20We%20can%20only%20hope%20for%20this%2C%20for%20there%20is%20little%20else%20in%20current%20party%20politics%20in%20India%20that%20seems%20remotely%20close%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAshish%20is%20with%20Kalpavriksh%2C%20Pune.%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707273021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F06183311%2FEffect-2024-02-06T183242.830.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcan-the-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-act-as-a-catalyst-for-deeper-transformation-in-our-democracy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20foregrounding%20economic%2C%20social%2C%20and%20political%20justice%2C%20the%20Yatra%20leaders%20are%20suggesting%20that%20their%20aspirations%20go%20beyond%20immediate%20electoral%20gains%20to%20achieve%20something%20more%20remarkable%2C%20possible%20only%20through%20a%20long-term%20goal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcan-the-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-act-as-a-catalyst-for-deeper-transformation-in-our-democracy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20Dismisses%20Byron%20Allen%E2%80%99s%20%24100%20Million%20Lawsuit%20Against%20McDonald%E2%80%99s%20Over%20Ad%20Spending%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707271683000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGettyImages-1990954248-e1707269769383.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235900412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20judge%20has%20dismisse