20Karachi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20narrative%20that%20charismatic%20populist%20leaders%20can%20bring%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cone%20man%20army%E2%80%9D%20revolution%20contributes%20to%20a%20shallow%20understanding%20of%20politics%2C%20Nizamani%20told%20Sapan%20News.%20This%20phenomenon%20is%20visible%20elsewhere%20too%2C%20like%20the%20USA%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Brazil%2C%20India%20and%20other%20countries%20with%20populist%20leaders%2C%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20demographics%2C%20youth%20aged%2015%20to%2029%20make%20up%2064%25%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhdr.undp.org%2Fcontent%2Funleashing-potential-young-pakistan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20UNDP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20although%2066%25%20of%2018-25-year-olds%20are%20registered%20voters%2C%20their%20voter%20turnout%20is%20much%20lower%20than%20the%20average%2C%20says%20Haris%20Gazdar%2C%20Director%20and%20Senior%20Researcher%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchcollective.org%2F%23about%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECollective%20for%20Social%20Science%20Research%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Karachi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20case%20even%20in%202018%2C%20and%20political%20parties%20%E2%80%9Chave%20not%20really%20had%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20youth%20voter%20registration%20and%20turnout%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20Sapan%20News.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThorny%20questions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGallup%20Pakistan%20found%20that%20the%20average%20voter%20turnout%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgallup.com.pk%2Fpost%2F32546%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20young%20people%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%2031.5%25%20in%202013%20and%202018.%20The%20figure%20for%20both%20years%20was%2040%25%