ons.%20Some%20even%20roasted%20the%20PM%2C%20asking%20why%20a%20technocratic%2C%20caretaker%20government%20was%20taking%20major%20policy%20decisions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20who%20held%20office%20with%20the%20previous%20government%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20youngest%20foreign%20minister%2C%20and%20former%20prime%20minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20have%20also%20interacted%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC-ZMgSwI5LM%3Fsi%3D8X9A0ny6Jw8U1863%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20students%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20various%20universities%20over%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhutto-Zardari%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20billed%20as%20%E2%80%9CAwami%20Muashi%20Muhaida%E2%80%9D%20(Public%20economic%20contract)%20takes%20up%20issues%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ede-corporatization%20of%20national%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esecurity%20systems%2C%20labourers%E2%80%99%20social%20security%2C%20access%20to%20education%20and%20financial%20support%20for%20youth%2C%20and%20climate%20resilience%20and%20energy%20transition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2035-year-old%20urges%20boomer%20politicians%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstay%20home%20and%20rest%2C%E2%80%9D%20make%20way%20for%20the%20younger%20generation%20to%20transform%20Pakistan%20into%20an%20exemplary%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20PML-N%20is%20campaigning%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20their%20previous%20development%20and%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20country.%20Projects%20they%20highlight%20as%20evidence%20of%20their%20commitment%20to%20the%20youth%20include%20the%20Danish%20Schools%20project%20established%20during%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20tenure%2C%20providing%20free%2C%20high-quality%20education%20to%20underprivileged%20children.%20Another%20project%20was%20the%20on-merit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Flaptop.pmyp.gov.pk%2Feligibility_criteria.php%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edistribution%20of%20laptops%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20students%20at%20public%20higher%20education%20institutes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20will%20these%20efforts%20translate%20into%20a%20better%20voter%20turnout%2C%20and%20will%20the%20parties%20play%20by%20their%20promises%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocial%20media-savvy%20Imran%20Khan%20is%20credited%20with%20having%20%E2%80%9Cawakened%E2%80%9D%20a%20generation%20of%20young%20people%E2%80%94a%20rhetoric%20which%20Gazdar%20of%20CSSR%20says%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20much%20of%20the%20street%20and%20social%20media%20presence%20of%20PTI%20is%20made%20up%20of%20young%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20overall%20voter%20registration%20and%20turnout%20rates%20even%20in%202018%20when%20the%20%E2%80%98system%E2%80%99%20favoured%20PTI%20remained%20low%20in%20the%2018-25%20group.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuppressing%20any%20party%20hinders%20political%20development%2C%20he%20notes%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Ca%20less%20noticed%20but%20more%20important%20issue%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20political%20engagement%20among%20large%20segments%20of%20the%20population%20including%20youth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20victimisation%20of%20Khan%20and%20his%20PTI%20has%20not%20decreased%20his%20support%2C%20and%20he%20is%20now%20likely%20to%20get%20more%20sympathy%20votes.%20A%20huge%20voter%20turnout%20on%20polling%20day%20may%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20deep%20state%20to%20change%20the%20results.%20Regardless%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20for%20Sharif%20to%20obtain%20the%20one%20third%20majority%20required%20to%20form%20government%20and%20a%20weak%20coalition%20government%20is%20on%20the%20cards%2C%20predict%20analysts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fsp