ery%20difficult%20to%20get%20a%20job%20anywhere.%20%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20while%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20graduates%20of%20psychology%2C%20there%20was%20no%20place%20for%20them%20to%20start%20their%20careers.%20This%20is%20how%20the%20Heal%20Grow%20Thrive%20Foundation%20came%20into%20being.%20Since%20we%20are%20self-funded%2C%20the%20therapy%20is%20done%20for%20a%20small%20fee%20but%20what%20we%20focus%20on%20is%20healing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20fleet%20of%2020%20young%20and%20budding%20therapists%2C%20she%20has%20helped%20over%20500%20survivors%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20patient%20of%20Mansi%20who%20prefers%20to%20be%20anonymous%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20talked%20to%20Mansi%2C%20she%20created%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20me.%20It%20was%20a%20space%20where%20I%20could%20really%20be%20%E2%80%98me%E2%80%99.%20I%20did%20not%20understand%20how%20much%20I%20needed%20the%20help%20until%20I%20took%20it.%20The%20best%20thing%20is%20that%20she%20focussed%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98why%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20turning%20to%20medication.%20Why%20was%20I%20feeling%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20why%20is%20the%20trauma%20so%20deeply%20rooted%2C%20and%20what%20I%20can%20do%20to%20help%20myself%3F%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20took%20the%20step%20for%20myself.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansi%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20focal%20point%20of%20my%20practice%20is%20to%20heal%20by%20processing%20things.%20As%20a%20survivor%20and%20a%20psychologist%2C%20I%20know%20how%20taking%20medicine%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20way%20out.%20However%2C%20I%20sincerely%20believe%20in%20trying%20everything%20in%20my%20power%20before%20referring%20patients%20to%20a%20psychiatrist.%20We%20believe%20in%20creating%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20the%20trauma%20survivor%20and%20helping%20them%20heal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20healing%20is%20not%20linear%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20I%20am%20an%20adul