portunities%20for%20skill%20development%20and%20employment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmbracing%20inclusive%20design%20principles%20ensures%20accessibility%20for%20individuals%20with%20disabilities%2C%20thereby%20contributing%20to%20creating%20a%20more%20equitable%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20innovation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Social%20innovation%20offers%20inventive%20technological%20solutions%20to%20societal%20issues%2C%20empowering%20local%20communities%20and%20addressing%20diverse%20needs.%20Prioritising%20sustainability%20and%20scalability%2C%20these%20innovations%20aim%20for%20enduring%20impacts%20adaptable%20to%20various%20situations%2C%20significantly%20contributing%20to%20multiple%20SDGs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollaborative%20partnerships%20among%20private%20entities%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20governments%20drive%20equity%20and%20extend%20development%20initiatives%20to%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20providing%20a%20boost%20in%20the%20race%20towards%20SDGs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollaboration%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Collaborative%20efforts%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20shared%20goal%20of%20leveraging%20technology%20for%20positive%20change%2C%20are%20crucial%20for%20SDG%20achievement.%20Bringing%20together%20expertise%20from%20governments%2C%20businesses%2C%20NGOs%2C%20academia%2C%20and%20communities%20allows%20for%20comprehensive%20problem-solving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20collective%20perspective%20on%20using%20digital%20innovation%2C%20data-driven%20solutions%2C%20and%20connectivity%20tools%20amplifies%20efforts%20to%20advance%20the%20SDGs%2C%20making%20collaboration%20the%20binding%20agent%20for%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20really%20struck%20me%20while%20building%20tech%20startups%20was%20the%20idea%20of%20how%20one%20could%20build%20an%20internet-based%20company%20to%20drive%20large-scale%20social%20change.%20Citizens%20want%20to%20be%20inspired.%20The%20need%20to%20be%20inspired%20is%20a%20universal%20need.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20storytelling.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20how%20you%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282876%2Frobinson-crusoe-island-taught-me-about-sustainability-storytelling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20a%20story%20relatable%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20average%20citizen%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dhimant%20Parekh%2C%20Founder%20and%20CEO%2C%20The%20Better%20India%20%E2%80%94%20one%20among%20the%20over%2080%20notable%20speakers%20and%20delegates%20present%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20message%20from%20the%20conclave%20is%20that%20combining%20technology%20with%20collaborative%20efforts%20can%20speed%20up%20progress%20in%20education%2C%20climate%20action%2C%20poverty%20reduction%2C%20and%20achieving%20at%20least%2070%25%20of%20the%20169%20SDG%20targets%20using%20data%20and%20digital%20technologies.%20This%20needs%20urgent%20action%20and%20a%20united%20effort%20from%20stakeholders%20like%20government%2C%20organisations%2C%20communities%2C%20and%20individuals.%20Effective%20strategies%2C%20policies%2C%20and%20initiatives%20are%20essential%20to%20accelerate%20the%202030%20agenda%20for%20sustainable%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20as%20a%20country%20is%20extremely%20committed%20to%20using%20technology%20and%20leveraging%20DPIs%20to%20fast-track%20the%20SDGs%2C%20and%20also%20to%20share%20our%20experiences%20and%20expertise%20with%20the%20global%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Abhishek%20Singh%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706796173000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDSC_4404-min_11zon-1706795984-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TechForGood%20India%20Concla