C%20with%20a%20semi-automatic%20option%20for%20special%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Scheduled%20water%20supply%3A%20Timings%20can%20be%20preset%20and%20valves%20open%20automatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Overflow%20Prevention%3A%20Installation%20of%20automatic%20mechanisms%20to%20stop%20overflow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Comprehensive%20data%20on%20water%20quantity%20and%20timings%2C%20enhancing%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20DC%20Sunkara%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20IoT%20system%20has%20already%20been%20successfully%20implemented%20in%2063%20OHTs%20in%2050%20habitations%20in%20Erode%20district%2C%20resulting%20in%20significant%20benefits%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20reduced%20motor%20running%20time%2C%20lower%20electricity%20bills%2C%20and%20minimised%20water%20wastage.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20reliability%20of%20water%20supply%20to%20the%20public%20has%20seen%20a%20remarkable%20improvement%3B%20thus%20alleviating%20the%20burden%20on%20women%20who%20often%20spend%20considerable%20time%20waiting%20near%20taps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20initiative%20costs%20roughly%20Rs%201%20to%201.5%20lakh%20per%20OHT%2C%20and%20has%20been%20mostly%20taken%20up%20under%20the%20village%20panchayat%20general%20fund%20or%2015th%20Central%20Finance%20Commission%20(CFC)%20funds.%20After%20the%20initial%20successes%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20installing%20it%20in%20150%20OHTs%20in%20Har%20Ghar%20Jal%20villages%20(all%20households%20in%20that%20village%20are%20provided%20with%20tap%20water%20supply)%20using%20these%20funds%20along%20with%20the%20District%20Mineral%20Foundation%20funds%2C%20Corporate%20Environment%20Responsibility%20funds%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.25-1706793757.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Residents%20in%20rural%20parts%20of%20Erode%20are%20dependent%20on%20the%20OHT%20water%20supply%20system.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.25-1706793757.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.25-1706793757-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.25-1706793757-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.25-1706793757-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.25-1706793757-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340521%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EResidents%20in%20rural%20parts%20of%20Erode%20are%20dependent%20on%20the%20OHT%20water%20supply%20system.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20this%20technology%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20linear%20level%20sensor%20pushes%20tank%20level%20alerts%20to%20the%20IoT%20Master%20Controller%2C%20triggering%20the%20pump%20and%20inlet%20valve%20to%20ensure%20OHT%20filling%20when%20water%20levels%20are%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20DC%20Sunkara.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20required%20level%20is%20reached%2C%20the%20motor%20switches%20off%2C%20and%20the%20inlet%20valve%20closes.%20The%20outlet%20valve%20operates%20automatically%20based%20on%20pre-set%20schedules.%20Real-time%20data%20generated%20from%20these%20functions%20is%20stored%20in%20AWS%20Cloud%20and%20can%20be%20accessed%20through%20the%20%3Cem%3EiNeer%20%3C%2Fem%3Emobile%20app%20by%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComprehensive%20data%20on%20water%20quantity%20and%20timings%20are%20collected%20in%20real-time%20through%20the%20sensors%2C%20which%20is%20made%20available%20on%20a%20mobile%20application%20to%20local%20public%20representatives%20like%20Panchayat%20presidents%2C%20tank%20operators%2C%20councillors%2C%20etc.%20The%20mobile%20application%20called%20%3Cem%3EiNeer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20(available%20on%20Google%20Play%20Store)%20provides%20insights%20into%20consumption%20patterns%20and%20operational%20efficiency%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBased%20on%20feedback%20from%20the%20stakeholders%2C%20the%20mobile%20application%20has%20been%20redesigned%20to%20make%20it%20very%20user-friendly.%20The%20impact%20on%20residents%20is%20reflected%20in%20improved%20water%20availability%2C%20reliable%20water%20timings%2C%20reduced%20waiting%20time%2C%20better%20water%20pressure%20and%20overall%20convenience%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20sure%20this%20system%20works%2C%20DC%20Sunkara%20notes%20how%20pilots%20were%20taken%20up%20in%20Kumaravalasu%2C%20Kuttapalayam%20and%20Ponmudi%20village%20panchayats%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Panchayat%20presidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20findings%20of%20these%20pilots%20were%20very%20encouraging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20But%20the%20administration%20did%20encounter%20challenges%20during%20the%20pilot%2Ftesting%20process%20including%20technical%20glitches%20and%20ensuring%20compatibility%20with%20existing%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20pilot%20stage%2C%20we%20planned%20for%20an%20electricity%20board%20(EB)%20supply%20for%20the%20IoT%20controllers%20and%20motorised%20valves.%20The%20controllers%20had%20to%20be%20chosen%20accordingly.%20The%20controllers%20got%20damaged%20during%20voltage%20fluctuations%20and%20lightning%20events.%20We%20then%20introduced%20a%20solar%20power%20supply%20with%20battery%20backup.%20The%20specifications%20for%20wattage%2C%20etc%20were%20finalised%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20each%20stage%2C%20it%20was%20a%20learning%20process%20for%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20implementation%20challenges%20included%20maintenance%20issues%20and%20the%20need%20for%20continuous%20monitoring%2C%20requiring%20collaboration%20with%20tech%20experts%20and%20regular%20training%20for%20maintenance%20staff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20public%20representatives%20like%20Panchayat%20presidents%20and%20Councillors%20were%20also%20trained%20in%20using%20the%20app%20through%20which%20OHTs%20can%20be%20controlled%20and%20data%20can%20be%20seen.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%2C%20there%20was%20some%20scepticism%20about%20the%20implementation%20of%20these%20IoT%20devices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitial%20scepticism%20was%20due%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20technology%20and%20since%20there%20was%20no%20precedent%20to%20learn%20from.%20While%20Panchayat%20presidents%20of%20the%20pilot%20villages%20took%20on%20this%20experiment%20with%20open%20minds%2C%20the%20other%20presidents%20were%20brought%20on%20board%20by%20arranging%20visits%20to%20see%20the%20success%20of%20the%20initiative%20in%20pilot%20villages.%20This%20helped%20overcome%20this%20scepticism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201235px)%20100vw%2C%201235px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIoT-devices-working-in-real-time-1706793892.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221235%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IoT%20devices%20working%20in%20real-time.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIoT-devices-working-in-real-time-1706793892.jpg%201235w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIoT-devices-working-in-real-time-1706793892-300x136.jpg%20300w%2C%