esults%20for%20Ponmudi%20have%20been%20reflected%20in%20other%20villages%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Renuva%20Devi%2C%20Panchayat%20president%20of%20Kuttapalayam%20village%20also%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20we%20are%20not%20dependent%20on%20the%20tank%20operator.%20Water%20is%20automatically%20supplied%20to%20the%20public%20at%20pre-set%20timings.%20There%20have%20hardly%20been%20any%20complaints%20regarding%20water%20supply%20from%20the%20public.%20Fixed%20quantity%20is%20being%20supplied%20for%20a%20fixed%20timing%20and%20then%2C%20there%20are%20water%20savings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20systems%20also%20helped%20alleviate%20the%20burden%20on%20women%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20from%20households%20with%20no%20direct%20water%20supply%20connections%20who%20often%20spend%20a%20long%20time%20waiting%20near%20taps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20society%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20fetching%20water%20falls%20on%20women.%20Water%20is%20supplied%20through%20household%20connections%20or%20public%20fountains%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20these%20connections%20or%20who%20are%20not%20getting%20adequate%20quantities%20of%20water%20through%20such%20connections%20were%20either%20forced%20to%20purchase%20water%20in%20the%20private%20market%20or%20wait%20at%20public%20fountains.%20The%20burden%20on%20women%20was%20further%20aggravated%20because%20of%20unreliable%20water%20supply%20timings.%20They%20would%20have%20to%20wait%20at%20odd%20timings%20and%20for%20long%20periods%20for%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20DC%20Sunkara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COut%20of%204%2C18%2C981%20households%2C%203%2C56%2C101%20have%20connections%20under%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20and%20works%20are%20ongoing%20for%20giving%20functional%20household%20tap%20connections%20to%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20