etterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20School%20for%20The%20Blind%20and%20Visually%20Impaired%20is%20located%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20School%20for%20The%20Blind%20and%20Visually%20Impaired%20is%20located%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Anand%20was%20excited%20to%20get%20on%20board%20the%20project%2C%20he%20lacked%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration.%20To%20find%20that%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20the%20kids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20began%20observing%20how%20students%20navigate%20through%20different%20places%20and%20spaces%2C%20identifying%20their%20preferences%20and%20gathering%20spots.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20made%20friends%20with%20students%20to%20better%20understand%20their%20daily%20routines%2C%20likes%2C%20and%20dislikes%20within%20the%20existing%20school.%20Similarly%2C%20I%20engaged%20in%20discussions%20with%20teachers%20to%20explore%20ways%20to%20enhance%20the%20learning%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Anand%20also%20started%20to%20visit%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338824%2Fmuskaan-dreams-abhishek-dubey-introduces-technology-in-rural-school-education-digital-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20schools%20for%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20visual%20impairment%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Victoria%20Memorial%20School%20for%20the%20Blind%20in%20Mumbai%20left%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20me%20because%20of%20its%20remarkable%20beauty%2C%20despite%20being%20an%20adaptively%20reused%20building.%20However%2C%20I%20found%20very%20few%20good%20examples%20of%20schools%20specifically%20designed%20for%20users%20with%20disabilities.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20I%20later%20volunteered%20at%20the%20Perkins%20School%20for%20the%20Blind%20in%20Massachusetts%2C%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20schools%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Established%20in%201829%2C%20it%20boasts%20a%20rich%20history%20with%20stalwarts%20like%20Helen%20Keller%2C%20Laura%20Bridgman%2C%20and%20Anne%20Sullivan%20who%20all%20studied%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20wonderful%20mentors%20in%20the%20US%20and%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20right%20direction%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20went%20out%20looking%20for%20inspiration%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20it%20was%20not%20one%20place%20that%20could%20help%20me%20but%20a%20lot.%20Visiting%20various%20schools%20was%20a%20great%20learning%20arc%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20five%20senses%20to%20navigate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20navigated%20with%20the%20help%20of%20four%20senses%3A%20sight%2C%20hearing%2C%20touch%2C%20and%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnly%2015%25%20of%20people%20with%20blindness%20experience%20a%20complete%20lack%20of%20sight.%20The%20majority%20of%20individuals%20who%20are%20blind%20may%20perceive%20light%20or%20colour%2C%20and%20those%20with%20different%20impairments%20have%20varying%20degrees%20of%20usable%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20walls%20have%20different%20textures%20for%20students%20to%20recognise%20the%20classes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340122%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20walls%20have%20different%20textures%20for%20students%20to%20recognise%20the%20classes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20Anand%20designed%20a%20school%20that%20uses%20colour%2C%20smell%2C%20and%20light%20to%20distinguish%20each%20class.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETouch%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20employed%20five%20different%20types%20of%20wall%20plasters%20and%20textures%20for%20students%20to%20identify%20spaces.%20Additionally%2C%20for%20ease%20of%20navigation%2C%20we%20utilised%20different%20textures%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20incorporating%20rough%20and%20smooth%20Kota%20stone%2C%20which%20marks%20the%20entry%20points%20of%20the%20classrooms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20area%20classroom%2C%20corridor%2C%20and%20courtyard%20in%20the%20school%20is%20marked%20and%20written%20in%20Braille.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHearing%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20another%20navigation%20technique%20that%20utilises%20hearing%2C%20Anand%20varies%20the%20volumes%20and%20heights%20of%20the%20buildings%2C%20creating%20different%20echoes%20and%20sounds%20to%20assist%20students%20in%20identifying%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20school%20features%20a%20wide%20and%20tall%20volume%2C%20while%20the%20opposite%20side%20has%20a%20shorter%20volume%20and%20is%20narrower.%20This%20contrast%20in%20width%20and%20height%20produces%20a%20distinct%20echo%20compared%20to%20the%20entrance.%20Students%2C%20as%20part%20of%20their%20training%2C%20walk%2C%20talk%2C%20and%20even%20clap%20to%20practise%20using%20different%20techniques%20for%20identifying%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20navigation%20easy%20for%20students%20who%20can%20perceive%20colour%20in%20light%2C%20he%20used%20different%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20that%20many%20low%20vision%20students%20are%20studying%20in%20the%20school%2C%20another%20aspect%20we%20had%20to%20consider%20was%20using%20contrasting%20colours%20and%20lighting%20to%20help%20students%20identify%20objects%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320628%2Fheta-pandit-writes-stories-from-goan-homes-book-on-culture-family-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efurniture%2C%20and%20spaces%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20each%20classroom%20door%20is%20brightly%20painted%2C%20the%20entrance%20is%20in%20a%20different%20bright%20colour%2C%20and%20the%20toilet%20doors%20are%20painted%20in%20contrasting%20yet%20vibrant%20colours.%20This%20approach%20ensures