20to%20make%20learning%20engaging%20and%20fun.%20Overcoming%20some%20initial%20trolling%2C%20Dhiraj%E2%80%99s%20follower%20count%20rose%20from%20160%20on%207%20December%202023%20to%201%20million%20on%2020%20January%202024%E2%80%94barely%2044%20days%E2%80%94on%20Instagram.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%201%20million%20followers%20today%2C%20Dhiraj%20has%20risen%20out%20of%20obscurity%20through%20his%20creativity%2C%20passion%20and%20desire%20to%20improve%20his%20communication%20skills%20by%20teaching%20others%20how%20to%20talk%20like%20a%20native%20English%20speaker%20despite%20lacking%20the%20resources%20that%20most%20content%20creators%20possess.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20Dhiraj%20to%20dig%20a%20little%20deeper%20into%20his%20magical%20journey%20on%20the%20internet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2TyPKJABP-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2TyPKJABP-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2TyPKJABP-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Dhiraj%20Takri%20(%40dhirajtakri)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELockdown%20opportunity%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20studying%20at%20a%20local%20village%20school%20till%20matriculation%20(Class%2010)%2C%20Dhiraj%20went%20to%20a%20nearby%20town%20to%20complete%20his%20intermediate%20(high%20school)%20but%20failed%20his%20Class%2012%20examinations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThings%20at%20home%20weren%E2%80%99t%20easy%20because%20our%20financial%20situation%20was%20unstable.%20My%20father%20used%20to%20repair%20bicycles%20while%20my%20mother%20travelled%20from%20one%20village%20to%20another%20selling%20bangles%20and%20other%20kinds%20of%20jewellery.%20After%20taking%20my%20Class%2012%20exams%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Kerala%20for%20a%20year%20where%20I%20lived%20and%20studied%20at%20a%20Christian%20theological%20training%20institute%20in%20Thiruvalla%2C%20Kerala.%20The%20only%20requirement%20to%20study%20there%20was%20a%20matriculation%20certificate.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20his%20parents%20are%20unemployed%20but%20his%20elder%20brother%20runs%20a%20local%20Jan%20Seva%20Kendra%20(common%20services%20centre).%20These%20centres%20assist%20residents%20access%20essential%20services%20online%20such%20as%20Aadahaar%20and%20PAN%20card%20services%2C%20payment%20of%20household%20bills%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20a%20two-year%20course%2C%20he%20only%20studied%20there%20for%20a%20year%20because%20of%20the%20national%20lockdown%20imposed%20following%20COVID-19.%20It%20was%20at%20this%20institute%20where%20he%20started%20learning%20English.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20regular%20access%20to%20our%20mobile%20phones.%20Every%20Saturday%2C%20they%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20use%20our%20phones%20for%20three%20hours.%20Back%20then%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20smartphone.%20I%20had%20a%20Jio%20phone%20with%20basic%20features.%20During%20one%20such%20session%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20video%20%5Bon%20YouTube%5D%20where%20I%20found%20someone%20teaching%20how%20to%20connect%20words%20and%20shorten%20them%20in%20spoken%20English%20conversation.%20That%20captivated%20me%20and%20I%20was%20interested%20to%20learn%20that%20kind%20of%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Dhiraj%20left%20Kerala%2C%20he%20began%20learning%20the%20%5BAmerican%5D%20accent%20that%20he%20currently%20employs%20in%20his%20reels%20by%20watching%20a%20plethora%20of%20videos%20online.%20Also%2C%20by%20the%20time%20he%20came%20back%20home%20to%20his%20village%2C%20he%20had%20a%20basic%20Panasonic%20P91%20smartphone%20with%20a%204G%20internet%20connection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20motivation%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20speak%20English%20in%20that%20manner%20came%20from%20a%20desire%20to%20communicate%20faster.%20As%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20used%20to%20speak%20English%20very%20slowly.%20Learning%20how%20to%20speak%20in%20an%20%5BWestern%5D%20accent%20was%20more%20about%20learning%20to%20speak%20the%20language%20faster.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20an%20interest%20in%20singing%20English%20songs%20like%20those%20in%20the%20West%20do.%20If%20I%20wanted%20to%20sing%20in%20their%20accent%2C%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20speak%20in%20their%20accent%20too.%20At%20the%20institute%20in%20Kerala%2C%20I%20developed%20a%20strong%20interest%20in%20learning%20the%20English%20language%2C%20and%20the%20desire%20to%20speak%20it%20faster%20and%20in%20a%20Western%20accent.%20But%20since%20our%20access%20to%20mobile%20phones%20was%20limited%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%9