5th%20Republic%20Day%2C%20132%20people%20were%20awarded%20national%20honours%20%E2%80%94%205%20Padma%20Vibhushan%2C%2017%20Padma%20Bhushan%2C%20and%20110%20Padma%20Shri%20Awards.%20Among%20these%2C%20Parbati%20Barua%2C%20now%20in%20her%20late%20sixties%2C%20received%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20her%20groundbreaking%20contribution%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F18228%2Fthe-only-female-mahaut-in-the-world-parbati-has-been-taming-wild-elephants-assam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20first%20female%20elephant%3C%2Fa%3E%20mahout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335631%2Fassam-jorhat-transwoman-opens-free-libraries-for-queer-positivity-lgbt-empowerment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20raised%20in%20Assam%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3EParbati%20disliked%20playing%20with%20dolls.%20Instead%2C%20she%20admired%20wildlife%20and%20enjoyed%20being%20outdoors.%20She%20was%20one%20of%20nine%20children%20born%20to%20the%20late%20Prakritish%20Chandra%20Barua%20of%20the%20Royal%20Family%20of%20Gauripur.%20Prakritish%20was%20the%20final%20ruler%20among%20the%20Rajahs%20of%20Gauripur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20young%20age%2C%20her%20affection%20for%20the%20gentle%20giants%20stemmed%20from%20her%20father%2C%20who%20was%20renowned%20internationally%20for%20his%20expertise%20and%20knowledge%20of%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFondly%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EHasti%20Kanya%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20Parbati%20captured%20her%20first%20elephant%20at%20the%20age%20of%2014%20in%20the%20Kachugaon%20forests%20of%20the%20Kokrajhar%20district.%20After%20this%20initial%20encounter%2C%20there%20was%20no%20stopping%20her.%20Defying%20all%20stereotypes%2C%20she%20became%20a%20mahout%20in%201972%20and%20dedicated%20herself%20to%20rescuing%20elephants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20daily%20routine%20involves%20giving%20her%20elephants%20baths%2C%20riding%20them%20in%20the%20jungle%2C%20and%20training%20them.%20She%20also%20mentioned%20making%20%3Cem%3Ehadiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20rice-based%20treat)%20for%20her%20beloved%20elephants%2C%20who%20have%20a%20fondness%20for%20liquor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5BThe%20elephants%5D%20love%20me%20because%20I%20understand%20their%20sentiments.%20One%20call%20and%20they%20all%20come%20running%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Parbati%20in%20an%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParbati%20has%20three%20pachyderm%20daughters%3A%20Lakshmimala%2C%20Aloka%2C%20and%20Kanchanmala.%20This%20trio%2C%20along%20with%20a%20team%20of%20dedicated%20coworkers%2C%20leads%20an%20unusual%20and%20adventurous%20life.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20job%2C%20there%20are%20no%20retakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20I%20go%20to%20the%20forests%2C%20I%20think%20of%20it%20as%20my%20last%20trip.%20But%20as%20a%20mahout%2C%20I%20can%20never%20retire.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStates%20like%20Bihar%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Assam%20seek%20her%20assistance%20in%20handling%20rogue%20tuskers%20or%20caring%20for%20those%20injured%20or%20ailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Parbati%20gained%20prominence%20and%20even%20became%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20BBC%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90580%2Fnotes-to-my-father-vr-documentary-sex-trafficking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edocumentary%20titled%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98Queen%20of%20the%20Elephants%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20her%20various%20tales%20of%20adventure%20is%20one%20from%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Midnapore%20district%2C%20where%20a%20herd%20of%2050%20elephants%20had%20lost%20their%20way%20and%20was%20on%20a%20destructive%20path.%20State%20authorities%20turned%20to%20Parbati%2C%20and%20with%20her%20three%20elephants%20and%20a%20team%20of%20other%20mahouts%2C%20they%20could%20guide%20the%20tuskers%20along%20the%20correct%20migratory%20trail%20after%20a%20fortnight%20of%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20on%20this%20adventurous%20path%2C%20Parbati%20leads%20a%20life%20devoid%20of%20modern%20conveniences%20even%20today.%20She%20uses%20ash%20instead%20of%20toothpaste%20and%20sleeps%20inside%20a%20tent%20on%20a%20threadbare%20mattress%2C%20while%20surrounded%20by%20the%20tools%20of%20her%20trade%20%E2%80%94%20ropes%2C%20chains%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhukris%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20sharp%20knife)%2C%20and%20stirrups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20asked%20about%20her%20fascination%20with%20the%20tuskers%2C%20she%20said%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EFirstpost%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CLove%20cannot%20be%20explained.%20Perhaps%20it%E2%80%99s%20because%20elephants%20are%20very%20stable%2C%20loyal%2C%20affectionate%20and%20disciplined.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706512063000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339899%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parbati%20Barua%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Hasti%20Kanya%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20female%20mahout%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20Padma%20Shri%20on%20Republic%20Day%2C%202024.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20elephants%20and%20dedicated%20her%20life%20to%20the%20gentle%20giants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339899%2Fpadma-shri-parbati-barua-queen-of-elephants-first-female-mahout-of-india-assam-west-bengal%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zero%20Plastic%2C%20Zero%20Toxins%3A%20This%20Student%20Designed%20Smart%20Eco-Friendly%20Air%20Fresheners%20Using%20Waste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20COVID-19%20struck%20the%20country%2C%20numero